ounting Firm","ttcExamples":["Managed daily bookkeeping functions with attention to accounts receivable, accounts payable, banking reconciliation and disbursements.","Compiled audit reports for expenditures, profits and losses to provide transparency.","Assisted internal accounting team in checking financial statements for accuracy to produce reliable reports.","Utilized automation system to process payments and invoices to streamline transactions.","Prepared month-end closing entries for detailed reporting and recordkeeping."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrative Assistant","company":"Small Business","ttcExamples":["Reviewed purchase documents and company receipts for reconciliation with statements.","Maintained full compliance when executing and tracking bank reconciliations, A/P, invoicing, billing and collections.","Prepared accurate financial reports each month by collecting, analyzing and summarizing account information.","Helped businesses keep finances in order by managing accounting ledgers and recording journal entries.","Prepared financial reports by collecting, analyzing and summarizing account information and trends."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrative Assistant","company":"Physician\'s Office","ttcExamples":["Cleaned and disinfected exam tables, trays and lamps to comply with infection control policy.","Received and screened telephone calls and visitors by determining or addressing needs.","Submitted diagnosis and procedure codes for insurance companies.","Maintained smooth flow of examinations to keep appointments on schedule.","Communicated with patients to resolve inquiries, schedule appointments and address billing questions."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrative Assistant","company":"Any Office","ttcExamples":["Wrote professional business correspondence to maintain strong line of communications.","Trained and mentored administrative staff members in company policies, daily task execution and industry best practices.","Managed office budget to handle inventory, postage and vendor services.","Interpreted and communicated work procedures and company policies to staff.","Reduced financial discrepancies by accurately managing accounting documentation while maintaining case costs and billing processes."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrative Assistant","company":"Investment Company","ttcExamples":["Made travel arrangements by booking hotels, flights and reservations.","Organized personal and professional calendars with reminders for upcoming meetings and events.","Worked closely with high-profile clients to provide one-on-one administrative support.","Maintained clerical correspondence via email and phone.","Screened telephone calls and inquiries and directed as appropriate."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrator","company":"Financial Services Company","ttcExamples":["Aligned systems with business needs to enhance scalability of database structures and recommend improvements.","Created and monitored performance metrics to keep databases functioning at optimal capacity.","Solved complex analytical problems using statistical models from data.","Uploaded antivirus software to protect data from cyber threats and malware.","Analyzed database applications and made necessary adjustments to parameters and architecture to improve performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrator","company":"Consumer Product Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Built and developed lasting relationships with employees, peers, upper management and outside vendors.","Developed and maintained resources and materials to support hiring managers throughout onboarding life cycle.","Leveraged internal HR databases to organize and maintain personnel records, enter employee data and update previous data.","Liaised between employees and benefit providers, serving as resource to answer benefit-related questions.","Worked with HR department to devise and update policies as needed for corporate accountability and workplace health."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrator","company":"Distribution Organization","ttcExamples":["Performed routine troubleshooting and network monitoring.","Installed and supported hardware and software for desktops, servers and printers.","Provided troubleshooting and testing to support network.","Created accounts and configured hardware to support onboarding process for new hires.","Strengthened networks and infrastructure during outage windows to prevent downtime for essential services."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrator","company":"Non-Profit Organization","ttcExamples":["Interacted professionally with customers and inside personnel, answering questions and responding to phone and email inquiries.","Prepared and made daily deposits and assisted with invoice processing and bank reconciliation.","Reviewed documents and obtained additional information to complete accurate paperwork and avoid delays.","Created memos, letters and other documents, fostering internal and external communication.","Collaborated with administrative support to oversee calendars and prioritize meetings and appointments."]},{"jobTitle":"Administrator","company":"Bank","ttcExamples":["Reviewed, investigated and corrected errors and inconsistencies in financial entries, documents and reports.","Collaborated with employees and supervisors to immediately resolve discrepancies in timesheets.","Researched and resolved employee payroll questions and issues via email, phone and in person.","Leveraged payroll processing system to track and input tax, wage and personnel information.","Supported payrolls, driving timely and accurate payment of employee wages."]},{"jobTitle":"Advisor","company":"Hair Salon","ttcExamples":["Recommended merchandise based on expert product knowledge and client preferences.","Stayed up-to-date on current and emerging trends to increase professional value and meet diverse client needs.","Showed customers how to apply makeup and other products to achieve desired looks.","Recommended treatment and styling products to customers to meet current needs or resolve specific concerns.","Built and deepened productive and positive customer relationships with high-quality service and focus on gaining loyalty."]},{"jobTitle":"Advisor","company":"Software Company","ttcExamples":["De-escalated problematic customer concerns, maintaining calm, friendly demeanor.","Answered incoming calls and emails, providing frontline customer support or assistance with product and service transactions.","Developed strong customer relationships to encourage repeat business.","Promoted high customer satisfaction by resolving problems with knowledgeable and friendly service.","Explained benefits, features and recommendations to maximize client retention."]},{"jobTitle":"Advisor","company":"Financial Services Company","ttcExamples":["Interviewed clients to determine income, expenses, financial objectives and risk tolerance in order to develop successful financial plans.","Developed and expanded financial planning relationships with customers through loyal and dedicated service.","Counseled clients on profitable strategies to support informed decision-making on investments, financing and partner sourcing.","Evaluated investment materials to develop financial recommendations, fulfill customer needs and predict favorable investments.","Assisted clients with planning for and funding retirements using mutual funds and other strategies."]},{"jobTitle":"Advisor","company":"Insurance Company","ttcExamples":["Communicated with clients by phone and email to answer questions and offer services.","Educated and counseled clients about insurance coverage differences and results of decisions to persuasively sell maximum coverage within budget.","Promptly responded to reported claims by communicating with customers and reporting information.","Answered insurer questions regarding policyholders.","Conducted research to identify ideal coverage options for customers."]},{"jobTitle":"Advisor","company":"Healthcare Services Company","ttcExamples":["Answered requests and concerns with friendly and knowledgeable service.","Analyzed territory and market potential regularly to identify and capitalize on growth opportunities.","Leveraged CRM system to manage sales activities and track sales performance.","Used active listening and relationship-building skills to assess customer needs, build rapport and connect with viable solutions.","Developed customized sales techniques to successfully sell and upsell services to new and existing clients."]},{"jobTitle":"Agent","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Utilized active listening and communication skills to address customer inquiries and escalate issues to supervisor.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions.","Delivered fast, friendly and knowledgeable service for routine questions and service complaints.","Reviewed files, records and other obtained documents to respond to customer requests.","Returned customer calls in established turnaround time to meet company objectives."]},{"jobTitle":"Agent","company":"Hotel or Office","ttcExamples":["Posted charges, updated accounts and issued bills to departing guests.","Greeted incoming guests warmly, issued room keys and shared information on policies and amenities.","Enhanced guest satisfaction by answering inquiries about business operations and policies, resolving concerns and developing creative solutions to guest concerns.","Answered telephones and greeted visitors to assist, answer questions and direct.","Responded to inquiries and room requests made online, by phone and via email."]},{"jobTitle":"Agent","company":"Insurance Company","ttcExamples":["Engaged customers and provided high level of service by carefully explaining details about documents.","Analyzed customer needs and provided best options, upselling products and services.","Pursued new clients through various marketing strategies to grow existing portfolio of policyholders.","Conducted meetings or phone calls with potential clients to present insurance policies and answer questions.","Stayed abreast of industry changes to amend insurance programs for existing and prospective clients."]},{"jobTitle":"Agent","company":"Realtor","ttcExamples":["Showed residential properties and explained features, value and benefits of available homes.","Advised prospective clients on current market activities and optimal buying or selling choices.","Planned and coordinated open house events to move properties.","Oversaw and negotiated offers for real estate purchases on clients\' behalf.","Promoted property sales through advertisements, open houses and participation in multiple listing services."]},{"jobTitle":"Agent","company":"Service Company","ttcExamples":["Answered customer questions and responded quickly to problems and complaints in person, on phone and by email.","Applied strategic communication strategies and interpersonal skills to develop and maintain high-value business relationships.","Offered product and service consultations and employed upselling techniques.","Regularly met or exceeded established sales goals by implementing strategic closing techniques.","Reviewed files, recordings and other documents to obtain information to respond to requests."]},{"jobTitle":"Analyst","company":"Business Consulting Firm","ttcExamples":["Defined key data points and data sources to track against measurable performance indicators and produce useful reports.","Identified and analyzed user requirements, procedures and processes to develop optimization strategies.","Remained current on latest IT developments and advancements to automate and modernize systems.","Uncovered areas for improvement to develop and implement solutions.","Utilized internal and external feedback to document business requirements."]},{"jobTitle":"Analyst","company":"Financial Lending Organization","ttcExamples":["Reviewed customer financial data to ascertain level of risk involved for extending credit.","Reconciled customer accounts to identify delinquencies or disputes, documenting root causes.","Prepared basic and preliminary credit analyses to determine creditworthiness and compliance.","Negotiated payment plans with customers, achieving sales and cash flow objectives.","Conducted credit reviews on corporations to assess financial conditions."]},{"jobTitle":"Analyst","company":"Data Services Company","ttcExamples":["Audited internal data and processes to identify and manage initiatives, improving business performance.","Generated reports and obtained data to develop analytics on key performance and operational metrics.","Synthesized business intelligence or trend data to support recommendations for action.","Conducted data analysis to prepare forecasts and identify trends.","Collected, tracked and reviewed data to evaluate business and market trends."]},{"jobTitle":"Analyst","company":"Investment Services Firm","ttcExamples":["Generated financial reports to garner forecasting, trending and narrative results analysis for management.","Worked cross-functionally with internal departments to align and validate data inputs.","Supported projects and analyses to drive consistency and accuracy within financial models.","Analyzed complex financial information to offer recommendations to management, driving decision-making.","Summarized financial information to clearly relay concepts and drive understanding of non-financial leaders."]},{"jobTitle":"Analyst","company":"Manufacturing Company","ttcExamples":["Identified quality trends to investigate system flaws, process inefficiencies and training needs.","Monitored completed work and provided feedback to improve team member performance.","Identified training opportunities to drive increased levels of quality through various projects.","Leveraged Six Sigma principles to identify and communicate compliance risks and quality improvement opportunities.","Participated in calibration sessions with stakeholders to promote consistent alignment on policies and processes."]},{"jobTitle":"Apprentice","company":"Commercial Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Listened to directives of senior electrical professionals to complete efficient tasks.","Kept work areas clean, neat and free of hazards.","Assisted with electrical installation tasks, added new wiring and adjusted breaker boxes.","Reviewed blueprints and electrical schematics to perform tasks to specifications.","Completed semi-skilled and skilled work under supervision of fully qualified professionals."]},{"jobTitle":"Apprentice","company":"Electrical Utility Company","ttcExamples":["Assisted in various capacities during construction, repair and maintenance of electrical lines.","Assessed power lines, poles and electrical equipment for wear and damage and reported deficiencies to appropriate supervisor.","Shortened or lengthened wires by removing or adding wire and used different types of splices, connectors and clamps.","Patrolled lines and reported defective equipment or unsafe conditions to supervisor for resolution.","Troubleshot overhead distribution lines to restore power service."]},{"jobTitle":"Apprentice","company":"Automotive Service Company","ttcExamples":["Supported lead mechanic by completing routine repair work, changing tires and replacing batteries","Worked alongside technicians providing regular service, troubleshooting and upgrading equipment.","Ordered parts, tools and supplies to stock shop and prepare for repair jobs.","Inspected and test drove vehicles before returning to customers.","Supported lead mechanic by completing routine repair work, changing tires and replacing batteries."]},{"jobTitle":"Apprentice","company":"Commercial Builder","ttcExamples":["Cut materials on job site to prepare for installation.","Cleaned job site after work completion and disposed of debris in proper containers.","Followed OSHA and corporate safety regulations and procedures.","Helped with movement of materials and equipment to different job sites.","Installed, assembled and repaired woodwork, millwork, cabinetry and trim under supervision of master carpenter."]},{"jobTitle":"Apprentice","company":"Plumbing Services Company","ttcExamples":["Operated tools and equipment such as hand saws, pipe cutters and drills on daily basis.","Maintained neat and well-organized worksites by removing debris and sharp objects and cleaning up after shift.","Assisted with installation of systems, components and construction materials into new and remodeled buildings.","Arranged and transported supplies needed for individual plumbing jobs and unloaded truck upon arrival.","Identified and located required tools prior to starting each project."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Provided secretarial and office management support while building cooperative working relationships.","Composed correspondence, reports and meeting notes.","Scheduled appointments, meetings and events for management staff.","Monitored office equipment and scheduled repairs.","Utilized editing programs to proofread content for typo-free emails, memos and documentation."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant","company":"Dental Practice","ttcExamples":["Sanitized equipment, cleaned treatment rooms and restocked supplies after each patient\'s treatment to maintain cleanliness and prepare for next patient.","Laid out dental instruments and equipment before procedures.","Educated patients on treatment procedures and post-procedure home care.","Gathered and reviewed patient records, data and health history to share with dentists for quick and accurate patient assessments, diagnosis and treatment.","Entered patient data into dental records system and observed confidentiality rules to maintain patient privacy."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant","company":"Nursing Facility","ttcExamples":["Answered signal lights, bells and requests-for-service to assist patient services fulfillment.","Documented nursing assessments, treatments and follow-up care to maintain patient safety and optimize workflow.","Assessed vitals and noted medical information to report changes to nursing staff and physicians.","Managed supplies and restocked inventory to promote optimal availability for patient care.","Maintained sanitary conditions by providing immediate wound care and dressing changes."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant","company":"Medical Office","ttcExamples":["Monitored calendars and scheduled appointments based on availability and established load limits.","Dispersed incoming mail to correct recipients throughout office.","Collected payments, issued receipts and updated accounts to reflect new balances.","Maintained business records by updating customer information.","Checked office supply levels, anticipated needs and placed orders for appropriate stock levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant","company":"Educational Organization","ttcExamples":["Contributed to positive, educational setting by delivering gentle discipline and promoting student success.","Discussed assigned duties with classroom teachers to coordinate instructional efforts.","Helped students master assignments and reinforced learning concepts presented by teachers.","Instructed and monitored students in use and care of equipment and materials.","Tutored and assisted children individually and in small groups to help master assignments and reinforce learning concepts."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Manager","company":"Corporate Office","ttcExamples":["Trained team members in administrative procedures and <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Software]</span> tasks to keep team efficient and consistent.","Collected and coded various documents to prepare for filing, storage and processing.","Distributed memos and updates to apprise departments and divisions of corporate objectives and developments.","Enforced company policies and procedures to strengthen operational standards across departments.","Monitored office inventory to maintain supply levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Manager","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Trained workers in food preparation, money handling and cleaning roles to facilitate restaurant operations.","Assisted personnel with duties and tasks during high-volume periods.","Calculated inventory and ordered appropriate supplies to meet expected demands.","Enforced and adhered to high-standards of cleanliness and organization throughout work and serving areas to remain compliant with company policies and regulatory requirements.","Took immediate responsibility for issues and found effective solutions for swift resolution."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Manager","company":"Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Helped sales professionals finalize customer sales and handled escalated concerns.","Met with team on weekly basis to identify sales opportunities, discuss strategies and execute new promotions.","Developed effective sales team members through highly individualized coaching.","Sourced and onboarded well-qualified inside and outside salespeople to enhance revenue generation.","Collaborated closely with management team to recruit top-level sales talent to fill positions within department."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Manager","company":"Grocery Store","ttcExamples":["Answered customer questions and addressed problems and complaints in person and via phone.","Supervised cashiers in processing credit, debit and cash payments to streamline sales.","Handled scheduling for store shifts to achieve adequate staffing.","Completed frequent walk-throughs and directed team members to correct issues impacting store appearance or professionalism.","Oversaw aspects of maintenance, inventory and daily activity management."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Manager","company":"Distribution Center","ttcExamples":["Completed periodic inventory counts and maintain accurate warehouse system.","Inspected equipment for functionality issues and arranged service actions when needed.","Created work schedules to keep warehouse shifts properly staffed. ","Drove forklift to transport items within warehouse or to pick up items from different locations for shipment.","Recommended changes to improve warehouse operational performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Store Manager","company":"Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Supervised bank deposits and inventory receipts as part of closing procedures.","Inspected store interior and exterior to check merchandise presentation and proper signage.","Interviewed job applicants and selected skilled individuals to fill store positions.","Delegated tasks and communicated expected deadlines to team members, supervising task completion.","Observed team members interacting with customers and privately offered feedback and coaching to improve skills."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Store Manager","company":"Home Improvement Retail Company","ttcExamples":["Completed periodic inventory counts and maintain accurate warehouse system.","Inspected equipment for functionality issues and arranged service actions when needed.","Created work schedules to keep warehouse shifts properly staffed. ","Drove forklift to transport items within warehouse or to pick up items from different locations for shipment.","Recommended changes to improve warehouse operational performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Store Manager","company":"Grocery Store","ttcExamples":["Assessed food store for cleanliness and checked proper stocking of shelves, refrigerated section and freezers.","Analyzed store\'s inventory and ordered merchandise and products to keep stock level.","Coordinated efficient restocking of grocery merchandise to meet customer needs and promote consistent sales.","Distributed daily tasks to appropriate employees and checked to complete duties within expected time frames.","Maintained comprehensive compliance with workplace and food safety standards to protect staff and customers."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Store Manager","company":"Big Box Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Received, evaluated and scanned in new inventory, updated computer database and proactively resolved variances.","Trained and developed staff on proper receiving, processing and stocking procedures.","Monitored inventories on computer to generate accurate reports.","Examined levels of supplies and material to determine shortages.","Analyzed stock levels and processes to predict inventory problems and formulate solutions."]},{"jobTitle":"Assistant Store Manager","company":"Consumer Electronics Retailer","ttcExamples":["Designed floor layouts, product displays and shelving layouts to maximize sales and influence customer purchasing habits.","Placed prices and descriptive signage to enhance displays and promote items.","Executed multiple projects simultaneously, coordinating and prioritizing tasks.","Used historical and current business data to determine key buying trends and items.","Collaborated with marketing team to develop and launch targeted strategies and initiatives."]},{"jobTitle":"Associate","company":"Online Retail Sales Organization","ttcExamples":["Supported customer service goals and enhanced relations through friendly, knowledgeable and positive communication.","Addressed inquiries, resolved customer issues and managed customer relations.","Delivered fast, friendly and knowledgeable service for routine questions and service complaints.","Educated customers on special pricing opportunities and company offerings.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions."]},{"jobTitle":"Associate","company":"Hotel ","ttcExamples":["Answered phones to respond to customer inquiries and transferred calls to appropriate staff members.","Managed guest check-in and check-out procedures, reservations and payments.","Delivered friendly and knowledgeable support to current and prospective customers.","Verified and collected client payments.","Answered phone and emails to make reservations and take guest information."]},{"jobTitle":"Associate","company":"Online Fulfillment Center","ttcExamples":["Accepted, processed and quickly filled orders.","Operated handheld scanners to track merchandise throughout fulfillment process.","Verified items correctly matched to sales check for packing and shipment.","Coordinated with other associates on day-to-day work activities to drive productivity and achieve operational objectives.","Unloaded merchandise from trucks and moved to designated areas for inspection and stocking."]},{"jobTitle":"Associate","company":"Big Box Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Welcomed customers, offered to help locate items and suggested merchandise without being intrusive or pushy.","Stocked and cleaned shelves while maintaining neat and orderly store.","Arranged merchandise for display to highlight new styles, attract customers and enhance sales.","Monitored sales floor to identify customers in need of assistance and merchandise requiring replenishment.","Counted cash, made change and stored coupons to keep organized and balanced cash register drawer."]},{"jobTitle":"Associate","company":"Manufacturing Organization","ttcExamples":["Moved large and bulky items manually or with pallet jacks or forklifts.","Staged and sorted multiple types of products for loading.","Used pallet jacks to move items to and from warehouse locations.","Loaded trucks for outbound orders and unloaded trucks for inbound orders.","Staged and sorted multiple types of products for loading."]},{"jobTitle":"Attendant","company":"Commercial Airline","ttcExamples":["Demonstrated safety equipment and procedures to meet FAA guidelines.","Anticipated needs of passengers to enhance comfort and promote enjoyable flight.","Administered and coordinated emergency procedures or care, enhancing onboard safety.","Attended trainings in customer service, conflict resolution techniques and safety procedures to remain current on new requirements and procedures.","Kept cabin neat, clean and professional in appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"Attendant","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Demonstrated proficient knowledge of menus, services and promotions to assist customers and team members.","Operated cash registers to handle both cash and card transactions, providing customers with appropriate change and receipts.","Replenished stocking stations with utensils, condiments and napkins.","Selected food items from serving or storage areas and placed on dishes or in serving trays or takeout bags.","Assembled and served meals according to specific guest requirements."]},{"jobTitle":"Attendant","company":"Gas Station","ttcExamples":["Processed payments via cash, credit and debit cards and counted back change to customers to avoid cash drawer errors.","Attended to gas spills and accidents promptly and according to established guidelines.","Maintained adequate food and beverages in display cases and refrigerators for customer convenience.","Inspected identification to determine proper age of customers for alcohol and cigarettes.","Prepared daily records of food and gas sales and balanced register drawers."]},{"jobTitle":"Attendant","company":"Hotel ","ttcExamples":["Furnished guests with clean linens and supplied rooms with toiletries.","Reported guest issues, safety and maintenance concerns immediately to supervisor.","Mapped out daily cleaning work assignments by assessing vacant room roster.","Removed soiled linens and articles from rooms and delivered to laundry area.","Polished and sanitized floors, counters, bathtubs and window sills."]},{"jobTitle":"Attendant","company":"Commercial Laundry Organization","ttcExamples":["Received and marked articles for laundry, identifying code numbers or names, using hand or machine markers.","Adhered to safety practices to decrease laundry-related accidents.","Applied specific treatments to handle different types of stains.","Moved loads between machines, operated ironing equipment and folded laundered items.","Transported laundry in carts and sorted dirty items by load type."]},{"jobTitle":"Babysitter","company":"Private Employer","ttcExamples":["Balanced schedules to promote optimal rest, play and educational periods.","Communicated with parents about daily activities and any concerning behaviors.","Cared for <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> children ages <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> to <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span>.","Organized and planned age-appropriate reading, crafts and music lessons.","Employed positive guidance strategies to encourage children and improve behavior."]},{"jobTitle":"Babysitter","company":"Preschool","ttcExamples":["Assisted lead teacher with snack time, arts and crafts and putting children down for naps.","Monitored children\'s play activities to verify safety and wellness.","Supported children\'s emotional and social development with one-on-one attention.","Used clear communication and professionalism to develop constructive relationships with families.","Established and maintained safe play environment for children."]},{"jobTitle":"Babysitter","company":"Daycare Center","ttcExamples":["Sanitized toys and tables to maintain clean, safe environment.","Assisted children in development of social, communication and problem-solving skills.","Used positive reinforcement and behavior modeling to instill discipline in children.","Communicated with parents about daily activities and any concerning behaviors.","Secured indoor and outdoor premises to protect children."]},{"jobTitle":"Babysitter","company":"Child Care Center","ttcExamples":["Developed and enforced positive strategies to encourage good behavior.","Prepared meals, snacks and refreshments for children according to dietary needs and restrictions.","Observed behavioral issues to alert parents or guardians.","Enforced rules to teach good manners and maintain safe environment.","Read aloud and played alphabet games to encourage early literacy."]},{"jobTitle":"Babysitter","company":"Professional Services Organization","ttcExamples":["Interacted positively with children to promote mental and emotional development.","Washed and put away dishes and wiped down counters after meals and snacks.","Physically and verbally interacted with children to promote mental and emotional development.","Encouraged safe, positive behavior by redirecting children to take positive action.","Engaged children with games and puzzles to promote mental development and enjoyment."]},{"jobTitle":"Barista","company":"Diner","ttcExamples":["Took inventory of supplies and equipment and placed new orders to maintain stock levels.","Developed menu items to help keep profits up and prices affordable for customers by balancing high and low food costs.","Rang up orders on cash register to process cash, credit card and personal check payments.","Trained new employees in operational procedures and modeled duties for front and back house positions.","Reconciled daily sales each shift, counting member drawers to analyze discrepancies."]},{"jobTitle":"Barista","company":"Outdoor Cafe","ttcExamples":["Protected staff and customers from infection by cleaning and sanitizing surfaces and equipment.","Rotated stock items and ingredients to maintain freshness.","Brewed coffee and tea for beverage area and restocked with paper goods, creamer and sugar.","Interacted pleasantly with customers and offered assistance to find needed items. ","Served patrons food from counters and steam tables."]},{"jobTitle":"Barista","company":"Coffeehouse","ttcExamples":["Kept coffee shop in compliance with health code standards and food safety guidelines.","Monitored employee performance and corrected errors impacting service, safety and profits.","Organized promotions to launch new coffee drinks and increase sales.","Reconciled daily sales each shift, counting register drawers and resolving discrepancies.","Oversaw food and beverage preparation to minimize waste and verify consistent presentation."]},{"jobTitle":"Barista","company":"Juice Bar","ttcExamples":["Followed drink recipes to make beverages by hand, with stick blenders and using machinery.","Prepared new garnishes, juices and other perishables daily.","Kept supplies stored in proper locations according to health code standards.","Used POS system to input orders, create checks and issue receipts.","Learned new formulas and menus to best serve customers with tasty drinks and current advice on selections."]},{"jobTitle":"Barista","company":"Chain Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Maintained accuracy while handling payments, giving change and printing receipts for customers.","Communicated with kitchen staff to stay updated on item availability and customer wait times.","Completed opening and closing checklists to ensure smooth restaurant operations.","Increased beverage sales with food and drink pairing suggestions to suit unique customer preferences.","Stocked server areas with supplies before, during and after shifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Bartender","company":"Sports Bar","ttcExamples":["Maintained detailed inventory of bar supplies and stocked work areas.","Completed thorough opening, closing and shift change functions to maintain operational standards each day.","Interviewed, hired and trained staff to improve customer retention and bolster sales.","Monitored patron alcohol consumption to encourage safety.","Planned and coordinated special events to boost customer numbers and profits."]},{"jobTitle":"Bartender","company":"Wine Bar","ttcExamples":["Stocked refrigerating units with wines or bottled beer and replaced empty beer kegs.","Maintained spotless, well-stocked bar organized and ready for customer demands.","Replenished bar glasses, garnishes and condiments.","Poured drinks using standard pour according to specifications.","Studied bartenders to learn recipes for different mixed cocktails."]},{"jobTitle":"Bartender","company":"Bar","ttcExamples":["Prepared both alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages for patrons.","Communicated with patrons to offer friendly service and determine needs.","Recommended and served alcoholic beverages to patrons during high-volume shifts.","Restocked bar with supplies for wide range of cocktails, beers and liquor drinks.","Mixed syrups following precise recipes to keep adequate supplies on hand."]},{"jobTitle":"Bartender","company":"Hotel Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Maintained accuracy while handling payments, giving change and printing receipts for customers.","Communicated with kitchen staff to stay updated on item availability and customer wait times.","Completed opening and closing checklists to ensure smooth restaurant operations.","Increased beverage sales with food and drink pairing suggestions to suit unique customer preferences.","Stocked server areas with supplies before, during and after shifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Bartender","company":"Entertainment Club","ttcExamples":["Received cash and card payments for balances owed.","Created unique cocktails for special events.","Used POS system to input orders, create checks and issue receipts.","Prepared new garnishes, juices and other perishables daily.","Crafted in-house made syrups, tinctures and speciality bar ingredients."]},{"jobTitle":"Business Owner","company":"Your Own Company","ttcExamples":["Devised business and marketing plans and prepared monthly financial reports.","Recruited and trained staff members to perform daily business functions.","Developed business plans to successfully finance business ventures.","Hired top-level talent and provided consistent mentoring, building strong management team.","Identified potential solutions to issues and implemented tactics to promptly resolve."]},{"jobTitle":"Business Owner","company":"Small Business","ttcExamples":["Balanced current and future operational demands to keep business growing and financially sound.","Sourced new talent to fill vacancies and help meet business objectives.","Prepared on-time and accurate documentation for tax filings, contracts and licensing.","Flexed between different roles daily to handle administrative, operational and financial needs.","Developed vision, mission and plan for business."]},{"jobTitle":"Business Owner","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Located relevant vendors, set up schedules and coordinated delivery, storage and organization of inventory.","Managed food preparation, guest interaction, quality control and customer relations.","Made weekly employee schedules, assigned work tasks and regularly checked quality and productivity of team members.","Administered finances and led business operations by running payroll, making bank deposits and analyzing income and expenses to maintain cost-effective operations.","Hired, trained and motivated staff to fill all restaurant openings."]},{"jobTitle":"Business Owner","company":"Boutique","ttcExamples":["Analyzed internal processes and implemented procedural or policy changes to improve operations.","Designed detailed business plans to outline finances, goals and operations of company.","Monitored financial objectives and prepared budgets according to projections.","Controlled shrinkage and product loss with monitoring and inventory management systems.","Trained employees according to specifics of role and company values."]},{"jobTitle":"Business Owner","company":"Sole Proprietorship","ttcExamples":["Prepared for new product lines and seasonal changes by running in-store and online clearance events.","Monitored and supervised customer\'s activities in store to detect signs of attempted theft.","Increased business by developing new marketing and promotional strategies.","Kept team on track by assigning and supervising activities and giving constructive feedback.","Implemented both individual and group training for executive and loss prevention personnel."]},{"jobTitle":"Carpenter","company":"Residential Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Cut materials on job site to prepare for installation.","Cleaned job site after work completion and disposed of debris in proper containers.","Followed OSHA and corporate safety regulations and procedures.","Helped with movement of materials and equipment to different job sites.","Installed, assembled and repaired woodwork, millwork, cabinetry and trim under supervision of master carpenter."]},{"jobTitle":"Carpenter","company":"Commercial Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Reviewed project plans and blueprints and estimating needed time and materials.","Trained and mentored employees, offering assistance and insight into completing job tasks when needed.","Followed OSHA and corporate safety regulations to avoid on-the-job injuries and accidents.","Delivered proper materials and equipment to job site in preparation for project.","Developed work schedules and delegated crew assignments, evaluating member performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Carpenter","company":"Carpet Company","ttcExamples":["Walked through jobs sites after installation to identify errors and completed rework to correct problems.","Met with customers to give free estimates on cost of installation and removal of existing flooring.","Created itemized, accurate paperwork detailing expected costs and timeframe for installation services.","Demonstrated protective coatings and odor treatments to upsell services and increase profits.","Operated and maintained company vehicle, keeping accurate records of mileage and service calls."]},{"jobTitle":"Carpenter","company":"Interior Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Installed and finished wood trim, doors and cabinets for new construction and renovation projects.","Produced high-quality work in full compliance with project standards and good carpentry practices.","Maintained high standards of workmanship with accurate, detail-oriented finishing work.","Promoted compliance with applicable federal, state and OSHA laws and regulations.","Completed custom woodwork for customers based on specifications."]},{"jobTitle":"Carpenter","company":"Builder","ttcExamples":["Measured and marked cutting lines on wood and raw materials.","Analyzed problematic installations and implemented appropriate solutions for quick remediation.","Fitted, cut and installed wood trim.","Reviewed and interpreted project specifications, determining tools and equipment needed.","Installed doors, frames and wood components following manufacturers\' instructions."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier","company":"Casino","ttcExamples":["Cashed out employee tips and worked with slot technicians to pay out jackpots.","Completed gaming forms and reports and assisted customers with credit-related problems.","Performed main banker duties by preparing deposits and accepting cash orders, preparing slot wallets and tills and consolidating cage transactions.","Prepared balance sheets in accordance with gaming standards and internal controls.","Counted, verified and posted armored car deposits."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier","company":"Retail Store","ttcExamples":["Greeted customers and responded to informational requests.","Handled customer complaints and concerns promptly, escalating complex issues to direct supervisor for quick resolution.","Processed credit card, EBT and gift certificate payments in electronic computer systems.","Maintained cleanliness and presentation of stock room and production floor.","Refilled and rotated items on shelves to maintain well-stocked inventory."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Restocked workstation with supplies and communicated out-of-stock items to management.","Reviewed contents on food trays to check complete order.","Completed opening, closing and shift change tasks by following company guidelines.","Boosted customer satisfaction by quickly addressing and resolving complaints with food or service.","Kept customer and food preparation areas clean and well-organized."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier","company":"Gas Station","ttcExamples":["Processed cash and credit payments for gasoline, food and other merchandise.","Cleaned store inside and out, straightened displays and maintained neat and inviting atmosphere for optimum customer satisfaction.","Checked customer ages before cigarette or alcohol purchases and allowed sale only if within legal age limits.","Counted cash in sales stations at shift beginning and verified enough cash to make change for customers.","Managed in-store food and general merchandise inventory, stocked goods and documented low stock levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier","company":"Big Box Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Monitored cash drawers in multiple checkout stations to confirm adequate cash supply.","Prepared cash deposits and balanced store safe for opening and closing of business.","Authorized discounts and special actions to resolve customer disputes and maintain satisfaction.","Screened applicants for hire and assisted with training individuals for cashier positions.","Managed employee scheduling according to availability, forecasted customer levels and labor cost controls."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier Team Lead","company":"Retail Store","ttcExamples":["Supervised counting cash drawers and made bank deposits as part of store opening and closing procedures.","Resolved customer problems by investigating issues, answering questions and building rapport.","Monitored cash drawers in checkouts to verify adequate cash supply.","Processed payments promptly for customers to exceed productivity standards.","Connected with customers to provide assistance and collect feedback to optimize operations."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier Team Lead","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Restocked workstation with supplies and communicated out-of-stock items to management.","Reviewed contents on food trays to check complete order.","Completed opening, closing and shift change tasks by following company guidelines.","Boosted customer satisfaction by quickly addressing and resolving complaints with food or service.","Kept customer and food preparation areas clean and well-organized."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier Team Lead","company":"Big Box Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Delivered consistent training and close mentoring support to front end employees in operations and customer service strategies.","Delegated work to employees based on shift requirements, individual strengths and unique training.","Handled payment processing and provided customers with receipts and proper bills and change.","Mentored employees in management of complicated sales, complex issues and difficult customers.","Cultivated professional relationships with guests, improving customer retention through coordinated service."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier Team Lead","company":"Retail Pharmacy","ttcExamples":["Monitored cash drawers in multiple checkout stations to confirm adequate cash supply.","Prepared cash deposits and balanced store safe for opening and closing of business.","Authorized discounts and special actions to resolve customer disputes and maintain satisfaction.","Screened applicants for hire and assisted with training individuals for cashier positions.","Managed employee scheduling according to availability, forecasted customer levels and labor cost controls."]},{"jobTitle":"Cashier Team Lead","company":"Clothing Store","ttcExamples":["Positively impacted product relevance through careful distribution, merchandising and display techniques.","Monitored loss prevention operations to minimize impact of shrink and identify theft and fraud.","Trained staff to have extensive product knowledge and upselling skills.","Processed sales transactions via cash register and telephone orders.","Cultivated loyal customer base by providing excellent customer service."]},{"jobTitle":"Certified Nursing Assistant","company":"Nursing Home Facility","ttcExamples":["Managed residents\' activities of daily living.","Kept room spaces, linens and restrooms clean and refreshed with supplies.","Supported individuals\' desires for dignity by compassionately assisting with personal hygiene.","Assisted patients with transportation and mobility needs such as moving between wheelchairs and beds.","Assessed patient needs and reported changes or issues to healthcare team."]},{"jobTitle":"Certified Nursing Assistant","company":"Home Health Agency","ttcExamples":["Assisted clients with bathing, dressing and incontinence care.","Followed HIPAA regulations to maintain confidentiality of sensitive patient information.","Documented care provided and submitted notes to supervisor.","Managed patient transportation and appointment scheduling.","Helped client with medication self-administration."]},{"jobTitle":"Certified Nursing Assistant","company":"Assisted Living Facility","ttcExamples":["Guided CNAs to complete work according to state standards, HIPAA requirements and internal practices.","Helped maintain welcoming environments for families, visitors and individuals under care.","Taught new CNAs how to complete ADLs and basic support work.","Enforced adherence to care and service plans and monitored team compliance with specifications.","Upheld infection control and prevention procedures with safe handling and disinfection protocols."]},{"jobTitle":"Certified Nursing Assistant","company":"Psychiatric Treatment Facility","ttcExamples":["Worked under supervision of registered nursing staff to deliver quality care to individuals in <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> setting.","Liaised between clinical and admissions teams on patient needs, providing clear communication about goals, progress and needs.","Observed and documented patient behavior accurately in Electronic Health Record (EHR).","Promoted patient safety, monitoring environment and behaviors to proactively identify concerns.","Applied therapeutic communication skills to engage patients, understand concerns and meet objectives of individual recovery plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Certified Nursing Assistant","company":"Private Nursing Agency","ttcExamples":["Redirected poor behavior using positive reinforcement.","Developed rapport to create safe and trusting environment for care.","Assisted clients with personal hygiene, bathing, grooming and dressing.","Engaged clients in age-appropriate activities and playing games.","Collaborated with guardians, physicians and teachers to establish individualized goals and build personalized treatment plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Charge Nurse","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Developed and initiated departmental goals, standards of performance, policies and procedures.","Managed clinical operations and procedures and enforced adherence to federal and state regulations and healthcare law requirements.","Interviewed applicants and made recommendations for new hires.","Interacted with patients, asked appropriate questions and listened carefully to deliver high level of clinical care.","Collaborated with healthcare professionals to deliver high-quality patient care."]},{"jobTitle":"Charge Nurse","company":"Outpatient Surgical Center","ttcExamples":["Mentored and coached nursing staff, listening to concerns and providing counsel.","Provided strong leadership and guidance to nurses.","Delegated clinical and managerial responsibilities to staff.","Completed comprehensive physical evaluations to prioritize treatments and make effective nursing assignments.","Collaborated with department managers to correct problems and improve services."]},{"jobTitle":"Charge Nurse","company":"Geriatric Care Facility","ttcExamples":["Administered medications in accordance with policies and legal limitations.","Educated patients on conditions, medications and self-care skills.","Observed and reported changes in condition of patients and signs and symptoms of deviations from normal health status.","Documented adverse patient reactions to medications and reported findings to supervisors.","Delivered emotional, psychological and spiritual support to patients and families to promote compassionate environment."]},{"jobTitle":"Charge Nurse","company":"Nursing Home Facility","ttcExamples":["Developed culture focused on meeting patient needs with team-oriented nursing approach.","Kept nursing team in compliance with Joint Commission standards and good practices for maximum patient satisfaction.","Acted promptly on identified issues impacting compliance, patient satisfaction or treatment quality.","Oversaw patient services for <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> area and adjacent oversight for related clinical and administrative services.","Built successful nursing team focused on delivering quality care, treatment and services to patients."]},{"jobTitle":"Charge Nurse","company":"Assisted Living Facility","ttcExamples":["Monitored infection control and critical incidents and made changes and improvements to processes where necessary.","Coordinated and led in-services to facilitate nursing leadership development and career growth.","Advised, coached and mentored experienced and student nurses on medical issues, crisis management and appropriate nursing interventions.","Partnered with organizational and unit leaders to devise QA/QI initiatives, continuously improving delivery of care, patient outcomes and overall services.","Oversaw multi-unit operations and addressed operational, staffing and care issues with immediate or long-term impacts."]},{"jobTitle":"Chef","company":"Private Services Agency","ttcExamples":["Focused on customer satisfaction, creating delicious cuisine to impress diners.","Created new menu items, managed food expenses and supervised quality to ensure adherence to standards.","Supervised <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> BOH staff members and delivered mentorship to strengthen kitchen skills.","Coordinated and executed menu planning, recipe development and daily restaurant operations.","Utilized local, fresh food products to support local economies and showcase community support."]},{"jobTitle":"Chef","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Regularly interacted with guests to obtain feedback on product quality and service levels.","Developed innovative recipes to suit complicated dietary requirements for customers.","Delegated tasks for kitchen employees and developed staff teams to streamline food preparation procedures.","Trained kitchen workers on culinary techniques.","Monitored quality, presentation and quantities of plated food across line."]},{"jobTitle":"Chef","company":"Bakery","ttcExamples":["Created <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> desserts such as cakes, frozen treats and pastries weekly.","Customized items for seasonal offerings, special events and personal requests.","Developed special menu items to improve business offerings.","Oversaw pastry production for catering, pick-up orders and in-store customers.","Placed dough in pans, molds and sheets and monitored products during baking to adjust temperature."]},{"jobTitle":"Chef","company":"Executive Support Services Agency","ttcExamples":["Cooked homemade meals using various techniques to enhance flavor and texture.","Created personalized meal plans based on client preferences, specifications, food allergies and dietary restrictions.","Crafted meals in clients\' home kitchens in accordance with food health and safety regulations.","Developed shopping lists in accordance with budgets provided by clients.","Built strong vendor relationships to bring in top ingredients at optimal prices."]},{"jobTitle":"Chef","company":"Chain Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Monitored food products, driving quality, freshness and integrity.","Oversaw kitchen employee scheduling to meet coverage needs and avoid wasted labor.","Directed staff in restaurant kitchen and field to maintain department objectives, standards, guidelines and budget.","Conducted frequent line checks to keep food at proper temperatures in holding zones.","Helped staff adhere to tough restaurant requirements through practical discipline and motivation."]},{"jobTitle":"Cleaner","company":"Airline Support Company","ttcExamples":["Vacuumed floors and cleaned aircraft\'s cockpit.","Washed, disinfected and restocked lavatories to meet usage demands.","Cleaned tray tables and windows and rearranged magazines to be presentable.","Removed exterior exhaust stains and washed down aircraft.","Removed trash from receptacles and seat pockets and replenished aircraft supplies."]},{"jobTitle":"Cleaner","company":"Professional Cleaners","ttcExamples":["Washed and polished glass windows and doors to keep entryways clear and professional.","Identified possible maintenance or safety issues and reported to supervisor and client.","Buffed tile floors and polished wall surfaces.","Replenished supply of hand soap, paper towels and other consumables.","Employed deep-cleaning techniques for areas in need of additional sanitation."]},{"jobTitle":"Cleaner","company":"Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Removed finger marks and smudges from doors, frames and glass partitions to enhance shine.","Requested maintenance orders to fix non-working equipment and address room damage.","Maintained and organized cleaning supplies stock.","Used cleaning chemicals following proper guidelines.","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"Cleaner","company":"Industrial Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Set up high-pressure pumps, vacuums and water-based systems to complete cleaning jobs.","Operated equipment safely to protect people and property from injury or damage.","Worked around in-operation machinery and with disassembled machinery to remove build-up and restore surfaces to desired cleanliness.","Inspected work sites and equipment to identify hazards or immediate work required to complete assignments.","Disassembled and cleaned equipment and individual components between jobs."]},{"jobTitle":"Cleaner","company":"Commercial Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Kept building interiors appealing with routine deep cleaning of high-traffic areas.","Handled, labeled and safely stored various hazardous chemicals and solutions to prevent injuries.","Dusted ledges, countertops, files, office equipment, desks and walls.","Notified building managers about needed repairs to maintain public safety.","Wet and spot mopped to clean floors and other surfaces in public corridors."]},{"jobTitle":"Clerk","company":"Grocery Store","ttcExamples":["Took unwanted items from checkout to proper location.","Packaged or bagged purchases and assisted customers with in-vehicle loading.","Oversaw collection shopping carts from parking lot to maintain clean, organized area.","Delivered exceptional customer service by greeting customers and directing to desired items.","Followed best practices for bagging items in reusable, plastic and paper bags."]},{"jobTitle":"Clerk","company":"Insurance Company","ttcExamples":["Input client information into spreadsheets and company database to provide leaders with quick access to essential client data.","Reviewed and updated account information in company computer system.","Identified and corrected data entry errors to prevent duplication across systems.","Responded to daily inquiries and requests within mandated timeframe to meet deadlines.","Scanned and stored files and records electronically to reduce paper files and secure data."]},{"jobTitle":"Clerk","company":"Delicatessen ","ttcExamples":["Checked signage and pricing to verify accurate displays on counters and in cases.","Sliced meats and cheeses and weighed deli items for customers.","Offered samples to promote and upsell specials.","Responded to customer questions regarding product availability.","Updated food displays, cases and other customer-facing areas to increase sales of special items."]},{"jobTitle":"Clerk","company":"Payroll Services Provider","ttcExamples":["Managed payroll for temporary, hourly and salaried employees.","Gathered timesheets to prepare weekly payroll data for processing by payroll coordinator.","Organized and maintained payroll information by entering data, deleting errors, calculating and collecting information.","Handled payroll help desk and answered questions regarding correct and accurate payroll time entry.","Protected payroll operations and maintained employee confidence by keeping information private."]},{"jobTitle":"Clerk","company":"Warehouse Operations Company","ttcExamples":["Operated forklifts, hand trucks, or other equipment to load, unload, transport and store goods.","Directed warehouse team in stocking merchandise, pulling orders and setting up loads.","Checked items to be shipped against work orders to confirm correct quantities, destination and routing.","Identified order discrepancies and damaged items and notified supervisor.","Prepared packages for shipping and determined most economical shipping methods."]},{"jobTitle":"Consultant","company":"Property Management Agency","ttcExamples":["Prepared lease paperwork and obtained signatures and first payments from new residents.","Promoted high level of customer service and assistance by greeting clients, responding to concerns, showing units and quickly resolving issues.","Conducted background checks on applicants.","Detailed application requirements and answered questions from prospective tenants.","Marketed property to prospective tenants by giving tours and pointing out key features."]},{"jobTitle":"Consultant","company":"Marketing Services Company","ttcExamples":["Researched clients and competitors to ascertain information useful for developing focused marketing solutions.","Supported clients in raising brand recognition through strategic marketing.","Spearheaded special event planning and design of conference materials, promotional items and booth setup.","Developed and implemented promotional plans targeting key audiences.","Recommended, planned and implemented promotional strategies to increase market share."]},{"jobTitle":"Consultant","company":"Big Box Retail Organization","ttcExamples":["Assisted with conducting merchandise stock counts and reported discrepancies to supervisor.","Used product knowledge to suggest items