 transparency, more accurate reporting and better identification of cost-saving opportunities.","Produced financial reports and audit documentation to facilitate internal and external auditing.","Supported asset transfers, lender and equity requests and audit inquiries.","Produced financial reports and audit documentation to facilitate internal and external auditing.","Advised executives on contracts with significant financial implications."]},{"jobTitle":"Controller","company":"Product Distribution Management Company","ttcExamples":["Investigated and resolved variances with inventory records.","Received incoming goods, checked paperwork and reviewed merchandise for accuracy against documentation.","Performed cycle counts on daily basis to immediately spot errors and apply remedies.","Researched inventory-related discrepancies and made appropriate adjustments in system.","Executed cycle counts of materials onsite and reconciled against company reports."]},{"jobTitle":"Controller","company":"Retail Sales Organization","ttcExamples":["Recorded merchandise moves for correct product counts and checked quantities against stocking reports.","Completed regular checks on stock levels and compared against forecasted demand.","Filled out paperwork and filed documents for new stock orders and damage claims.","Kept detailed records of previous purchases and standard prices for items.","Counted inventory with daily cycles and periodic full-scale audits."]},{"jobTitle":"Controller","company":"Public Highway Maintenance Organization","ttcExamples":["Directed vehicles around construction sites and flagged drivers through blocked roads.","Assembled traffic cones and pathways for vehicles and pedestrians.","Directed pedestrians across busy streets and around construction sites.","Managed setup and removal of temporary traffic control equipment and signs.","Monitored and coordinated traffic during power outages and emergencies."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Operated fryers and grills according to instructions to maintain safety and food quality.","Communicated with kitchen staff to complete orders quickly.","Wiped down counters with sanitizing spray to avoid contamination and foodborne illnesses.","Kept stations stocked and ready for use to maximize productivity.","Restocked and rotated food products using first-in, first-out method."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook","company":"Diner","ttcExamples":["Maintained cleanliness and organization of line workstations.","Stored foods in designated areas by following standard wrapping, dating and rotation procedures.","Distributed prepared food to servers.","Utilized kitchen utensils and equipment to weigh, measure and mix ingredients according to recipes or personal judgment.","Grilled various cuts of meat and seafood items to meet customer specifications and food handling standards.  "]},{"jobTitle":"Cook","company":"Chain Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Served as lead cook, guiding and assisting training of less experienced cooks.","Kept kitchen, cooking utensils and storeroom clean and neat.","Cut, chopped and sliced meat and produce to prepare for cooking.","Followed recipes and procedures to prepare, season and cook food products.","Communicated with kitchen employees, answered questions and offered insight into food preparations."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook","company":"Commercial Cafeteria","ttcExamples":["Followed proper food handling methods and maintained correct food temperature for high scores on health inspections.","Cleaned cooking and refrigeration equipment to sanitize and prevent food-borne illness.","Adhered to portion controls and presentation specifications.","Conducted daily inspections and maintained food sanitation and kitchen equipment safety reports.","Set up workstations with needed ingredients, utensils and cooking equipment."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Prepped vegetables and ingredients by washing, chopping and dicing.","Organized and labeled stock of ingredients to maintain needed inventory levels.","Measured and weighed food items to comply with portion requirements.","Completed special orders according to customer dietary needs.","Dressed, seasoned and garnished appetizers and salads to prepare for food service."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook\'s Assistant","company":"Chain Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Checked dates on food to maintain proper rotation, discarding expired items.","Worked with head chef to master cutting and preparation techniques.","Used commercial baking and cooking equipment.","Handled presentation standards and portion control requirements.","Assisted head chef by chopping and preparing cooking ingredients. "]},{"jobTitle":"Cook\'s Assistant","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Prepared dish ingredients by chopping vegetables, meats and garnishes.","Worked with team of <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> kitchen staff and delegated appropriate tasks to each member.","Rotated frozen and refrigerated food items with new deliveries to prevent spoilage.","Monitored food budget and purchased supplies according to available funds and expected demand.","Maintained kitchen order by thoroughly cleaning grills, stoves, counters and tables."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook\'s Assistant","company":"Commercial Food Service Provider","ttcExamples":["Monitored inventory to keep adequate stock of food items and supplies.","Prevented spoilage or cross-contamination by storing food in designated containers and areas.","Washed and sanitized plates using industrial dishwashers according to manufacturer instructions.","Operated industrial mixers and other food processing machinery to support kitchen operations.","Cleaned and sterilized dishes, countertops and utensils to prevent bacteria growth."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook\'s Assistant","company":"Institutional Food Service Company","ttcExamples":["Prepped vegetables and ingredients by washing, chopping and dicing.","Organized and labeled stock of ingredients to maintain needed inventory levels.","Measured and weighed food items to comply with portion requirements.","Completed special orders according to customer dietary needs.","Dressed, seasoned and garnished appetizers and salads to prepare for food service."]},{"jobTitle":"Cook\'s Assistant","company":"Healthcare Institution","ttcExamples":["Monitored food products, driving quality, freshness and integrity.","Oversaw kitchen employee scheduling to meet coverage needs and avoid wasted labor.","Directed staff in restaurant kitchen and field to maintain department objectives, standards, guidelines and budget.","Conducted frequent line checks to keep food at proper temperatures in holding zones.","Helped staff adhere to tough restaurant requirements through practical discipline and motivation."]},{"jobTitle":"Coordinator","company":"Event Management Firm","ttcExamples":["Participated in pre-event meetings to review expectations and security measures.","Developed diagrams and floor plans with event setup requirements.","Delivered client services in logistics, registration and attendee tracking for internal and external events.","Directed event production in collaboration with sponsors, hosts and internal teams.","Assessed event success and identified improvement areas through client feedback."]},{"jobTitle":"Coordinator","company":"Trucking Company","ttcExamples":["Logged, processed and followed up on merchandise authorization shipments in databases.","Dispatched information to service providers to schedule freight movement.","Relayed information between drivers and recipients regarding ETA and potential delays.","Managed paperwork and necessary information required for client shipments.","Identified root causes of service failures and implemented appropriate remediation measures to prevent future issues."]},{"jobTitle":"Coordinator","company":"Professional Services Organization","ttcExamples":["Developed brand marketing plan strategies to increase brand awareness.","Wrote, proofed and edited content in accordance with established brand guidelines.","Proposed internal and external ideas and initiatives to help promote general awareness of company brand.","Created daily social media posts to build robust brand presence on Twitter, Facebook and Instagram.","Collaborated with marketing manager to plan out campaign strategies, time tables and guidelines."]},{"jobTitle":"Coordinator","company":"Community Organization","ttcExamples":["Coordinated logistics for activities and events.","Scheduled and developed program activities in accordance with program needs.","Uncovered issues to determine solutions and assist program participants.","Explained program offerings and requirements to participants and answered related questions.","Developed and distributed brochures, newsletters and flyers for promotional literature."]},{"jobTitle":"Coordinator","company":"Software Company","ttcExamples":["Collaborated with internal teams to develop project solutions resulting in on-time execution.","Prioritized needs and delegated assignments to simultaneously handle multiple projects.","Produced status reports for customers and senior management.","Assessed, monitored and reported on work progression.","Managed portfolio of projects to drive on-time deliverables within scope and budget."]},{"jobTitle":"Counselor","company":"Youth Camp","ttcExamples":["Coordinated and led group activities for campers and counselors.","Engaged children in arts and crafts, singing, sports activities, games and field trips while maintaining safe environment.","Monitored activities matched to individual and group abilities to keep campers safe.","Established and built relationships with campers to ease fears in new environment.","Improved camper experience with list of flash-fun ideas."]},{"jobTitle":"Counselor","company":"Behavioral Health Practice","ttcExamples":["Referred clients to external resources for additional support.","Led patients in individual, family, group and marital therapy sessions.","Recorded comprehensive patient histories and coordinated treatment plans with multi-disciplinary team members.","Demonstrated sensitivity and competence in treating patients from diverse backgrounds.","Assisted clients with identifying feelings and behaviors by asking open-ended questions."]},{"jobTitle":"Counselor","company":"Residential Care Facility","ttcExamples":["Provided appropriate feedback and information to help residents succeed in program.","Responded to crisis situations quickly to maintain calm and immediately determine level of assistance needed.","Interfaced with residents to address and resolve complaints or grievances.","Fostered relationships with residents and worked with new residents to optimize acclimation and ease transition to new living environment.","Completed daily resident welfare checks and coordinated with facility staff to meet resident needs."]},{"jobTitle":"Counselor","company":"School","ttcExamples":["Promoted parent and teacher partnerships and communications to support students educational goals.","Placed students into academically appropriate classes after reviewing data and records.","Monitored students academic progress, mental health and sociability through ongoing individual assessments.","Placed students into academically appropriate classes after reviewing data and records.","Supported teachers and students during Individual Education Plan (IEP) development."]},{"jobTitle":"Counselor","company":"Rehabilitation Center","ttcExamples":["Conducted individual and group therapy sessions for outpatient clients.","Maintained thorough clinical treatment notes.","Identified treatment goals based on individual diagnosis and history.","Led supportive group discussions and education sessions with alcohol and drug users and families.","Identified problem areas impacting participants\' ability to successfully complete treatment."]},{"jobTitle":"Crew Member","company":"Commercial Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Wiped down various surfaces with approved cleaning products to prevent growth of bacteria and viruses.","Labeled and properly stored chemicals, equipment and cleaning products. ","Measured and mixed detergents with water for use in commercial cleaning. ","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance.","Dusted ceiling fans and air vents to eliminate dirt buildup. "]},{"jobTitle":"Crew Member","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Went above and beyond to help customers and meet needs, delivering exceptional customer service.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions.","Reviewed complaints and developed balanced solutions to resolve customer concerns.","Completed purchases for customers, issued tickets and advised on related policies and procedures.","Engaged customers in conversation to understand needs and suggested related products or services for upselling."]},{"jobTitle":"Crew Member","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Greeted customers to take food orders and provide information about menus.","Operated cash register and received payment from customers in cash or credit form.","Received inventory of food and beverage products to stock in designated areas.","Organized food items on serving trays and in carry-out packages.","Modified requested menu items in POS system to customize orders."]},{"jobTitle":"Crew Member","company":"Commercial Airline","ttcExamples":["Demonstrated safety equipment and procedures to meet FAA guidelines.","Anticipated needs of passengers to enhance comfort and promote enjoyable flight.","Administered and coordinated emergency procedures or care, enhancing onboard safety.","Attended trainings in customer service, conflict resolution techniques and safety procedures to remain current on new requirements and procedures.","Kept cabin neat, clean and professional in appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"Crew Member","company":"Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Performed repetitive assembly tasks with hand and power tools and automated equipment.","Completed variety of physical labor tasks.","Understood and followed oral and written directions.","Read plans, instructions or specifications to determine work activities.","Maintained clean, safe working environment by removing debris from job site prior to shift completion."]},{"jobTitle":"Custodian","company":"Facility Maintenance Company","ttcExamples":["Opened and closed building with necessary checks, alarms and door security.","Completed daily cleaning checklists for diverse range of spaces inside buildings.","Serviced kitchen and bathrooms with in-depth cleanings to sanitize spaces and restock supplies.","Checked on building equipment with thorough inspections, handled basic upkeep and reported serious concerns to management.","Handled seasonal maintenance work to keep parking lot and sidewalks free of debris and safety hazards."]},{"jobTitle":"Custodian","company":"Commercial Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Oversaw and facilitated general and preventive maintenance schedule across facility.","Monitored building access and secured premises by locking and unlocking entrances according to established schedule.","Reported or resolved observed hazards observed and followed up to verify resolution.","Established positive working relationships with staff, supervisors and building occupants.","Organized assignments and schedules for subordinates to cover daily and deep cleaning needs."]},{"jobTitle":"Custodian","company":"Public Transportation Organization","ttcExamples":["Used correct methods and approved cleaning products to prevent growth of bacteria and viruses on frequently touched surfaces.","Responded promptly to requests to clean and sanitize areas after accidents.","Maintained inventory of cleaning supplies and documented items requiring reorder.","Operated equipment according to safety guidelines to prevent damaging property.","Set up furniture following instructions to prepare spaces for events."]},{"jobTitle":"Custodian","company":"Healthcare Institution","ttcExamples":["Gathered and emptied trash cans and disposed of bags.","Sanitized and deep cleaned bathroom floors and surfaces.","Stored, used and disposed of cleaning chemicals and supplies.","Followed strict schedules, cleaning according to facility usage and room availability.","Wiped furniture and fixtures to remove dust and build-up."]},{"jobTitle":"Custodian","company":"School","ttcExamples":["Reset school spaces nightly with complete cleanings of bathrooms, hallways and cafeteria.","Detailed carpets weekly around corners, edges and under furniture.","Cleaned glass surfaces daily to remove hand prints and spots.","Re-positioned furniture into standard arrangements for student and staff use.","Dusted surfaces of desks, chairs and tables to maintain cleanliness."]},{"jobTitle":"Customer Service Representative","company":"Physicians\' Practice","ttcExamples":["Evaluated accounts for payment compliance and contacted customers.","Answered customer invoice questions and resolved issues discovered during invoicing and collection process.","Processed and sent invoices, adjustments and credit memos to customers.","Submitted claims to insurance companies and researched and resolved denials and explanations of benefit rejections.","Contacted vendors to follow up on late invoices."]},{"jobTitle":"Customer Service Representative","company":"Nonprofit Organization","ttcExamples":["Handled calls for new sign-ups, service cancellations and cross-selling opportunities.","Maintained knowledge of company products, services and procedures to better serve customers and meet company goals.","Completed transactions for membership renewals and extensions.","Offered exceptional customer service to differentiate and promote company brand.","Answered member questions about products and services."]},{"jobTitle":"Customer Service Representative","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Accessed patient information through various software applications, maintaining strict confidentiality to remain compliant with HIPAA regulations.","Scanned completed forms, identification and insurance cards, maintaining patient documents folder.","Documented and managed patient information in computer system.","Obtained proper authorization and identification to release confidential medical records.","Scheduled and confirmed patient appointments with patients and healthcare professionals."]},{"jobTitle":"Customer Service Representative","company":"Online Sales Organization","ttcExamples":["Cross-trained in multiple areas to support team members with high-volume task loads.","Offered promotional deals and loyalty program sign-ups to increase brand awareness.","Engaged with customers and recommended products based on needs and requests.","Answered questions about current promotions and resolved issues according to store policies.","Calculated pricing, applied discounts and collected payments to process transactions."]},{"jobTitle":"Customer Service Representative","company":"Computer Hardware Sales Organization","ttcExamples":["Supported customers with online billing, access and account issues.","Served as first point of contact for incoming technical service calls and emails.","Demonstrated advanced product knowledge to solve customer issues.","Used remote login tools to assist clients with technical and product questions.","Assisted customers with various types of technical issues via email, live chat and telephone."]},{"jobTitle":"Delivery Driver","company":"Big Brown Truck","ttcExamples":["Checked and secured package loads before deliveries.","Coordinated parcel delivery using strong time management skills.","Communicated with dispatchers, management and colleagues to form lasting partnerships.","Documented pickups and deliveries and submitted reports after shift.","Alerted customers to weather-related pickup or delivery delays."]},{"jobTitle":"Delivery Driver","company":"Beverage Distributor","ttcExamples":["Recorded numbers of units handled and moved on daily production sheets or work tickets.","Lifted boxes and products with correct safety gear and techniques.","Used hand truck to deliver heavy or multiple packages to business and residential locations.","Requested customer signatures for deliveries.","Mapped routes and specific locations using local road knowledge and GPS software."]},{"jobTitle":"Delivery Driver","company":"Online Food Delivery Service","ttcExamples":["Picked up meals from local restaurants and dropped off at residential and business customer locations.","Carried food in insulated bags to maintain hot or cold temperature.","Delivered fresh food to customers across local area.","Analyzed customer address to determine best route for timely delivery.","Communicated with restaurant staff to coordinate deliveries and obtain destination address."]},{"jobTitle":"Delivery Driver","company":"Automotive Dealership","ttcExamples":["Unloaded and organized inventory received from manufacturers and distribution centers.","Packaged and safely loaded parts and materials to prevent damage during transportation.","Pulled specific store parts from inventory and occasionally used dollies to load and unload heavy equipment from vehicles.","Obtained customer signature on receipt for pickup or delivery.","Strengthened customer relationships with prompt and professional service."]},{"jobTitle":"Delivery Driver","company":"Product Distributor","ttcExamples":["Drove vehicle along predetermined route and delivered customer orders on-schedule.","Followed DOT regulations and company safe driving guidelines and immediately reported safety hazards.","Maneuvered vehicle into position at warehouse for unloading returns and loading new deliveries.","Verified delivery of items with customers and obtained proper signatures.","Completed damage control checks on items and contacted supervisor about removing orders according to company policy."]},{"jobTitle":"Director","company":"Nursing Home Facility","ttcExamples":["Designed and led activities in crafts, music and sports.","Coordinated calendars, shifts and activity schedules with staff.","Interacted with patients and families by addressing questions and concerns.","Designed programs to encourage entertainment, relaxation, socialization and fulfillment for <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Business Name]</span>.","Trained and managed assistants and delegated tasks for staff members."]},{"jobTitle":"Director","company":"Inpatient Healthcare Facility","ttcExamples":["Implemented and directed clinical services and operations to deliver competent, quality care.","Developed and maintained staffing schedule in accordance with contract terms, budget mandates, and accreditation standards for nursing coverage.","Conducted recruitment and retention activities to develop highly skilled nursing team.","Assessed competency of clinical staff to promote quality, continuity and safety.","Reviewed daily documentation of dispensing of controlled substances, immediately noting discrepancies from shift to shift."]},{"jobTitle":"Director","company":"Marketing Services Company","ttcExamples":["Updated web pages and social media profiles with engaging and current content.","Developed and implemented strategic marketing campaigns, including site promotions and engaging digital content.","Executed updated marketing plans to increase branding exposure, customer traffic and sales.","Evaluated and enhanced content of online pages, blog posts and social media platforms.","Developed and deepened professional relationships with vendors, negotiated contracts and monitored performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Director","company":"Nonprofit Organization","ttcExamples":["Devised evaluation strategies to monitor performance and determine need for improvements.","Facilitated staff meetings and educational work sessions to strengthen staff competencies.","Wrote proposals and reports for general and specific program support.","Used evaluation outcomes and research to set program goals and determine strategy and direction.","Managed program operations and provided strategic leadership for workers."]},{"jobTitle":"Director","company":"Pharmaceutical Sales Company","ttcExamples":["Presented sales proposals to prospective customers to build new opportunities.","Coordinated action plans for sales team to penetrate new markets.","Collaborated with sales personnel to discuss strategies to close lucrative deals","Coached and mentored team members to build sales and negotiation skills.","Hired and trained talented employees to build valuable, skilled sales team."]},{"jobTitle":"Director Of Nursing","company":"Nursing Home Facility","ttcExamples":["Assessed competency of clinical staff to promote quality, continuity and safety.","Reviewed daily documentation of dispensing of controlled substances, immediately noting discrepancies from shift to shift.","Reviewed incident reports <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Timeframe]</span> for accuracy and proper notification to family, physicians and other agencies as required by regulations.","Oversaw explanation of personnel policies and job descriptions as part of nursing employee orientation process.","Implemented changes needed to correct deficiencies found during government inspections."]},{"jobTitle":"Director Of Nursing","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Mentored and coached nursing staff, listening to concerns and providing counsel.","Provided strong leadership and guidance to nurses.","Delegated clinical and managerial responsibilities to staff.","Completed comprehensive physical evaluations to prioritize treatments and make effective nursing assignments.","Collaborated with department managers to correct problems and improve services."]},{"jobTitle":"Director Of Nursing","company":"Geriatric Care Facility","ttcExamples":["Received and investigated complaints from families, patients and clinical staff, devising solutions to multifaceted challenges.","Improved patient outcomes through peer groups and facilitating continuing education.","Applied clinical judgment and comprehensive knowledge of facility policies to assist floor nurses with patient care decisions.","Performed personnel interviewing, hiring, disciplinary actions and dismissals.","Monitored staff performance and provided coaching and formal counseling to staff."]},{"jobTitle":"Director Of Nursing","company":"Healthcare Institution","ttcExamples":["Developed culture focused on meeting patient needs with team-oriented nursing approach.","Kept nursing team in compliance with Joint Commission standards and good practices for maximum patient satisfaction.","Acted promptly on identified issues impacting compliance, patient satisfaction or treatment quality.","Oversaw patient services for <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> area and adjacent oversight for related clinical and administrative services.","Built successful nursing team focused on delivering quality care, treatment and services to patients."]},{"jobTitle":"Director Of Nursing","company":"Inpatient Healthcare Facility","ttcExamples":["Monitored infection control and critical incidents and made changes and improvements to processes where necessary.","Coordinated and led in-services to facilitate nursing leadership development and career growth.","Advised, coached and mentored experienced and student nurses on medical issues, crisis management and appropriate nursing interventions.","Partnered with organizational and unit leaders to devise QA/QI initiatives, continuously improving delivery of care, patient outcomes and overall services.","Oversaw multi-unit operations and addressed operational, staffing and care issues with immediate or long-term impacts."]},{"jobTitle":"Dispatcher","company":"Municipal Government","ttcExamples":["Handled emergency phone calls calmly and obtained pertinent information with composed approach.","Used radio, telephone and computer system to update first responders with new information.","Prioritized responses to public emergency and non-emergent calls to promptly dispatch police, fire and EMS while tracking data in real-time.","Took caller information, read associated computer information and documented vital details in call tracking and assignment system.","Dispatched calls to relevant police, fire or medical response personnel depending on individual call situations."]},{"jobTitle":"Dispatcher","company":"Commercial Airline","ttcExamples":["Determined fuel supply requirements, coordinated with air traffic control and issued safety information and coordination with air traffic control.","Worked with customer service agents and aircraft routers to manage scheduling and cancellations.","Planned flights with consideration to meteorological conditions, aircraft discrepancies and performance limitations.","Prepared dispatch release documents for flights.","Facilitated positive interaction with flight crews, station managers and HQ through detailed reports and flight briefings."]},{"jobTitle":"Dispatcher","company":"Alarm Services Company","ttcExamples":["Collected pertinent information from callers to disseminate to responding units or agencies.","Investigated calls and complaints involving fire, theft, accident and hazard reports.","Used radio, phone or computer to direct crews and other field units to appropriate sites.","Answered telephone calls to take messages, respond to questions and provide information during non-business hours.","Monitored and authorized entrance and departure of employees and visitors to guard against theft and maintain security of premises."]},{"jobTitle":"Dispatcher","company":"Home Maintenance and Repair Company","ttcExamples":["Prioritized tasks and managed project adjustments to successfully manage high-volume service dispatching.","Issued purchase orders authorization to perform services and maintained accurate records.","Contacted technicians in afternoon to find out status for following morning and prepared start sheet.","Worked closely with lead technicians to handle scheduling, follow ups and recalls.","Created work orders in <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Software]</span> and assigned to correct dispatch boards for technicians or subcontractors."]},{"jobTitle":"Dispatcher","company":"Bus Transportation Company","ttcExamples":["Created schedules and dispatched drivers to various sites across coverage location.","Checked paperwork prior to dispatching crew members to maintain accuracy.","Responded to customer messages in regards to delivery issues.","Spoke with customers to ensure that expectations regarding deliveries had been met or exceeded.","Oversaw scheduled routes to ensure appropriate coverage by delivery drivers."]},{"jobTitle":"Driver","company":"Ambulance Company","ttcExamples":["Documented each transport with patient name, mileage and services rendered.","Sanitized medical equipment and inside of vehicle after each transport to avoid spread of germs.","Braced and lifted patients onto stretchers in preparation for medical transport.","Adhered to driving protocols and regulations to maximize safe transportation.","Delivered clear communication to dispatch and medical facilities and provided detailed information regarding patient conditions."]},{"jobTitle":"Driver","company":"Bus Transportation Company","ttcExamples":["Performed pre-trip inspection and mechanical checks before scheduled run.","Drove established routes and maintained knowledge of streets and stops to deliver positive passenger experiences.","Obeyed DOT rules and regulations and local laws to maximize safety.","Operated bus professionally and interacted with passengers to foster pleasant rides.","Transported passengers on predetermined routes while obeying traffic regulations."]},{"jobTitle":"Driver","company":"ABC Delivery Company","ttcExamples":["Utilized street maps to plan and determine most efficient routes.","Handled merchandise in accordance with product handling standards.","Loaded trucks and safely secured merchandise to prevent damage during transportation.","Inspected vehicle and maintained gas, oil and water levels.","Notified customers of delays to decrease calls to support."]},{"jobTitle":"Driver","company":"Online Transportation Company","ttcExamples":["Followed safety rules to keep clean driving record with no accidents or incidents.","Drove passengers from pick-up points to deliver to destination.","Cleaned vehicle regularly to maintain professional appearance.","Used advanced driving techniques to better improve time management and safety.","Offered riders information about local attractions and restaurants."]},{"jobTitle":"Driver","company":"Logistics Company","ttcExamples":["Hooked and unhooked trailers from tractor and converter dollies.","Drove tractor-trailer combinations to transport and deliver products, livestock or other materials.","Read and interpreted maps to determine vehicle routes.","Inspected truck for defects and safe operating condition before, during and after trips.","Delivered customer orders to homes and places of business within established time frames."]},{"jobTitle":"Executive","company":"Insurance Company","ttcExamples":["Optimized profitability by developing pipeline of prospects using multiple research, referral and sales strategies.","Facilitated and managed business development plan based on market and industry research.","Created value propositions, national programs and strategic plans for multi-location and national accounts.","Grew sales YoY by developing robust marketing plans and cultivating long-lasting industry partnerships.","Handled client accounts through entire lifecycle, executing contracts, providing customer service and advising on methods for maximizing return from services provided."]},{"jobTitle":"Executive","company":"Professional Services Organization","ttcExamples":["Coordinated meeting and work schedules for staff teams and executives.","Leveraged word processing software to create proposals, letters and memos.","Obtained signatures for financial documents and internal and external invoices.","Monitored office equipment and scheduled repairs.","Opened, read and replied to emails, letters and correspondence on behalf of executives."]},{"jobTitle":"Executive","company":"Multinational Business Operations","ttcExamples":["Created and implemented HR strategies and initiatives aligned with business objectives.","Maintained benefits program by leading decision-making process and upkeep.","Developed and oversaw performance appraisal systems to drive peak performance.","Directed recruitment, selection and hiring processes.","Evaluated training needs and oversaw training programs."]},{"jobTitle":"Executive","company":"Commercial Product Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Developed and implemented digital marketing plans to incorporate SEO, social media platforms and video campaigns.","Planned and organized public relations and promotional events.","Launched and managed targeted email marketing campaigns.","Expanded new businesses by developing powerful sales, advertising and marketing campaigns.","Identified, developed and evaluated marketing strategies based on knowledge of company objectives and market trends."]},{"jobTitle":"Executive","company":"Commercial Product Distributor","ttcExamples":["Exceeded sales goals and improved profitability by aligning sales strategies and business plans with market trends.","Sourced new sales opportunities through inbound lead follow-up.","Communicated regularly with territory and regional managers for daily support and strategic planning.","Contacted current and potential clients to promote products and services.","Developed and maintained records on customer contacts and used information to support effective follow-up opportunities."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Hand","company":"Commercial Agricultural Operation","ttcExamples":["Directed efficient crop production to maximize resource utilization and consistently meet schedule and financial demands.","Monitored weather conditions and adjusted strategies accordingly to avoid losses.","Protected environmental areas, team members and consumers from harm by closely monitoring chemical applications and production techniques.","Delegated tasks to seasonal workers and supervised completion of duties and responsibilities.","Applied knowledge of animal husbandry to meet livestock needs and minimize disease risk."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Hand","company":"Commercial Grower","ttcExamples":["Pruned and checked for pests to properly care for plants.","Adhered to safety protocols to minimize risk and avoid accidents.","Harvested crops and prepared for packaging or sale.","Troubleshot malfunctions and completed basic repairs on field equipment. ","Circulated through field to check plants for harvesting. "]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Hand","company":"Commercial Orchard Company","ttcExamples":["Identified, picked and sorted fruits according to size, type and ripeness.","Checked fruit for signs of disease or insects, reporting details to supervisor.","Transported barrels, baskets and crates of picked fruit to assigned areas.","Used hand tools, ladders and other equipment to complete assigned tasks efficiently.","Placed picked fruit in baskets, lining with protective wrapping."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Hand","company":"Commercial Stock Company","ttcExamples":["Cared for livestock and monitored health and living spaces.","Provided water, food, vaccinations and healthcare for livestock.","Operated ranch equipment for animal care and transport or field irrigation.","Maintained equipment with preventive maintenance and repairs.","Monitored grounds and reported damage or issues to supervisor before making repairs."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Hand","company":"Agricultural Farm","ttcExamples":["Assisted with maintenance and repair activities to keep buildings and equipment in safe and proper condition.","Watered and fed livestock and cleaned pens and enclosures to maintain farm animal health.","Completed harvesting activities using harvesters, tractors and other heavy equipment.","Monitored and adjusted irrigation systems to distribute water according to crop needs.","Sprayed fertilizer or pesticide solutions to control insects and fungus."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Laborer","company":"Commercial Agricultural Operation","ttcExamples":["Cared for livestock by regularly feeding and watering animals.","Repaired buildings, fences and other pertinent structures to keep animals properly contained.","Checked fields regularly to spot and handle broken fencing to keep out destructive animals.","Plowed and tilled fields to prepare soil for crop planting.","Moved full containers of crops to storage or immediate shipment areas using forklifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Laborer","company":"Commercial Stock Company","ttcExamples":["Promoted optimal animal health by feeding and watering on regular schedule.","Observed behavioral changes in animals to detect illness or injury.","Monitored safety of every animal to prevent injuries from other animals or environmental hazards.","Set boundaries through disciplinary teaching and treat training.","Followed consistent safety procedures, maintained visible animal identification and checked tags to minimize care errors."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Laborer","company":"Dairy Producer","ttcExamples":["Assisted with feeding, tagging and treating calves.","Patrolled, inspected and reported animal health and reported suspicious or unusual behavior.","Maintained high standards of animal welfare when performing feeding and milking procedures.","Washed and cleaned cattle udders, milk parlors and tanks.","Collaborated with veterinarians to provide medicine and vaccinations for sick animals."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Laborer","company":"Plant Grower","ttcExamples":["Routinely pruned and trimmed plants to promote healthy growth and remove diseases.","Swept and picked up trash in and around greenhouse.","Assisted with crop harvesting and transplantation.","Adhered to watering schedule to keep greenhouse plants healthy and well-maintained.","Planted seeds and bulbs after preparing soil and fertilizer appropriately."]},{"jobTitle":"Farm Laborer","company":"Plant Nursery","ttcExamples":["Applied fertilizer and pesticides to improve plant health and protect crops. ","Handled plants and shrubs with care to avoid damage.","Irrigated plants at specific intervals to moisten soil and promote growth.","Pruned, trimmed and culled plants to maximize proper growth.","Tied and wrapped plants in preparation for planting."]},{"jobTitle":"Foreman","company":"Builder","ttcExamples":["Reviewed project plans and blueprints and estimating needed time and materials.","Trained and mentored employees, offering assistance and insight into completing job tasks when needed.","Followed OSHA and corporate safety regulations to avoid on-the-job injuries and accidents.","Delivered proper materials and equipment to job site in preparation for project.","Developed work schedules and delegated crew assignments, evaluating member performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Foreman","company":"Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Managed daily work assignments by delegating tasks and monitoring progress.","Read and followed blueprints when planning and implementing construction phases.","Maintained quality standards and monitored work for corrective action.","Assigned projects and tasks to employees based on competencies and specialties.","Performed work safely and effectively in high and precarious places."]},{"jobTitle":"Foreman","company":"Electrical Contractor","ttcExamples":["Took ownership of electrical crew schedule, developing short- and long-term look-ahead schedules to align with execution plans.","Supervised job site operations to maintain consistent safety and hazard-free work area.","Followed electrical code manuals to install and repair electrical systems.","Installed, tested and modified circuit breakers, controls, fuses, lights and motors.","Communicated with clients to convey deadlines, scope of work and potential challenges throughout project timeline."]},{"jobTitle":"Foreman","company":"Landscape Company","ttcExamples":["Delegated tasks to landscaping crews and supervised completion.","Monitored job site safety and work quality of landscaping projects.","Reviewed blueprints and job specifications to determine manpower and equipment needed.","Inspected malfunctioning equipment and troubleshot issues, returning tools to operation.","Met with clients to discuss landscaping project process and deliver details regarding completion and proper plant care."]},{"jobTitle":"Foreman","company":"Machining Company","ttcExamples":["Scheduled maintenance and directed repairs on shop machinery and tools.","Managed team of <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> personnel focused in the shop and the field.","Coordinated materials for shop needs and field operations at work sites.","Trained and mentored employees in procedures and performance improvement strategies.","Implemented workplace safety protocols to minimize accidents and incidents."]},{"jobTitle":"General Manager","company":"Financial Services Company","ttcExamples":["Acted as main point of contact in matters relating to client concerns and needs.","Oversaw multiple accounts and worked diligently to meet and exceed performance goals.","Developed successful customer relationships and quickly resolved service requests to increase sales.","Negotiated agreements with clients for pricing and logistics.","Used CRM database to track referral and appointment data."]},{"jobTitle":"General Manager","company":"Business Services Provider","ttcExamples":["Established strong client relationships to drive business development.","Developed short-term and long-term vision and strategy to achieve targeted sales objectives.","Secured new opportunities from existing customers to maximize and enhance growth at each account.","Leveraged cold calling, in-person visits and referrals to build leads.","Prospected for new business by developing targeted solicitation plans for key accounts."]},{"jobTitle":"General Manager","company":"Trucking Company","ttcExamples":["Created and enforced policies and procedures for entire logistics team.","Troubleshot and formulated strategies for expected and unanticipated logistics issues.","Utilized ordering, tracking and billing systems and associated processes.","Consistently met company and department objectives within budget and time constraints.","Identified and resolved shipping and packaging errors."]},{"jobTitle":"General Manager","company":"Professional Services Firm","ttcExamples":["Developed social media marketing strategies to help brand company and increase sales.","Managed creation of marketing materials, collateral and sales support tools.","Formulated and launched marketing and promotional campaigns to maximize profits.","Conducted thorough market research to obtain detailed understanding of consumer needs and trends.","Evaluated and reported on campaign performance to relevant stakeholders and leadership across organization."]},{"jobTitle":"General Manager","company":"Manufacturing Company","ttcExamples":["Delivered positive customer experiences by implementing effective quality assurance practices.","Addressed customer concerns with suitable solutions.","Recruited, hired and trained crew members on application of projects, customer relations and customer service.","Directed day-to-day operations by spearheading implementation of short-term and long-term strategies to achieve business plan and profitability goals.","Built strong operational teams to meet process and production demands."]},{"jobTitle":"Helper","company":"Food Services Organization","ttcExamples":["Peeled and cut fruit and vegetables to prepare for cooking or serving.","Prevented spoilage or cross-contamination by storing food in designated containers and areas.","Cleaned and sterilized dishes, countertops and utensils to prevent bacteria growth.","Monitored inventory to keep adequate stock of food items and supplies.","Operated industrial mixers and other food processing machinery to support kitchen operations."]},{"jobTitle":"Helper","company":"Cleaning Agency","ttcExamples":["Employed deep-cleaning techniques for areas in need of additional sanitation.","Washed and polished glass windows and doors to keep entryways clear and professional.","Cleaned customer laundry according to care instructions for specific garments and articles of clothing.","Planned and prepared meals that met clients\' expectations and tastes.","Turned mattresses and changed sheets to freshen bedding."]},{"jobTitle":"Helper","company":"Package Delivery Company","ttcExamples":["Recorded numbers of units handled and moved on daily production sheets or work tickets.","Lifted boxes and products with correct safety gear and techniques.","Used hand truck to deliver heavy or multiple packages to business and residential locations.","Requested customer signatures for deliveries.","Mapped routes and specific locations using local road knowledge and GPS software."]},{"jobTitle":"Helper","company":"School","ttcExamples":["Helped students stow book bags, coats and other items in cubbies and lockers.","Assisted classroom teacher with preparing, typing, copying and filing learning materials.","Oversaw safety and well-being of students under care during teacher absences.","Prepared visual aids, equipment and classroom displays to foster learning.","Followed school schedules and policies to promote safety and learning."]},{"jobTitle":"Helper","company":"Welding Contractor","ttcExamples":["Brought supplies, equipment and tools to work locations.","Heated, formed and dressed metal parts with hand tools, torch and arc welding equipment.","Completed precision cuts with power saws, hand shears and chipping knives.","Heated, formed and dressed metal parts with hand tools, torch and arc welding equipment.","Examined final products for conformance with quality and design standards."]},{"jobTitle":"Home Health Aide","company":"Nonprofit Organization","ttcExamples":["Assisted terminally ill patients with bathing, grooming and dressing.","Helped patients maintain dignity during difficult times.","Measured vital signs, recorded data gathered and provided treatment assistance to nurses.","Moved patients carefully into different positions to promote better body alignment and comfort.","Supported grieving families by offering listening ear, compassion and kindness."]},{"jobTitle":"Home Health Aide","company":"Nursing Home Facility","ttcExamples":["Prevented spread of infection by consistent hand washing, universal precautions and special isolation procedures.","Safely and accurately prepared all medications and sterilized products by using proper techniques, calculations and standards of precautions.","Performed wellness observations, documenting side effects for clinical follow-up.","Liaised with nursing staff to prepare and administer prescribed medications to patients.","Leveraged medication expertise to accurately enter medications and supplies into computer system."]},{"jobTitle":"Home Health Aide","company":"Private Care Agency","ttcExamples":["Provided ongoing compassionate patient care for each client.","Monitored vital signs and medication use, documenting variances and concerning responses.","Helped clients with personal needs from exercise to bathing and personal grooming.","Developed strong and trusting rapport with patients to facilitate smooth, quality care.","Assisted with meal planning to meet nutritional plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Home Health Aide","company":"Orthopedic Practice","ttcExamples":["Collaborated with PT to assist in assessment and modifications to plan of care.","Worked with physical therapist and other disciplines to provide adaptive equipment for improving patient function.","Designed home exercise programs to support continuation of therapeutic plan.","Maintained positive interaction with facilities and clients, enhancing client relations.","Described therapeutic regimens to promote wellness and health maintenance."]},{"jobTitle":"Home Health Aide","company":"Home Health Agency","ttcExamples":["Redirected poor behavior using positive reinforcement.","Developed rapport to create safe and trusting environment for care.","Assisted clients with personal hygiene, bathing, grooming and dressing.","Engaged clients in age-appropriate activities and playing games.","Collaborated with guardians, physicians and teachers to establish individualized goals and build personalized treatment plans."]},{"jobTitle":"House Cleaner","company":"Residential Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Swept, mopped, waxed and vacuumed carpeted and hard surface floors.","Disposed of hazardous materials in appropriate containers.","Exceeded company standards for cleanliness, sanitation and presentation.","Partnered with housekeeping team to maintain compliance with OSHA requirements and risk management protocol.","Used dusting and polishing skills to leave clean and shiny appearance on surfaces."]},{"jobTitle":"House Cleaner","company":"Professional Cleaning Company","ttcExamples":["Sanitized frequented areas and equipment using approved supplies.","Dusted ceiling air conditioning diffusers and ventilation systems to improve airflow.","Vacuumed carpeted areas and mopped solid surfaces with proper chemical solutions.","Reported maintenance concerns or repairs to appropriate supervisor for prompt remediation.","Used shampoos and steam equipment to periodically clean upholstery and carpeting."]},{"jobTitle":"House Cleaner","company":"Private Employer","ttcExamples":["Removed finger marks and smudges from doors, frames and glass partitions to enhance shine.","Requested maintenance orders to fix non-working equipment and address room damage.","Maintained and organized cleaning supplies stock.","Used cleaning chemicals following proper guidelines.","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"House Cleaner","company":"Hotel ","ttcExamples":["Stocked room attendant carts with supplies to keep carts organized and clean.","Placed housekeeping staff on specific shifts and room blocks based on abilities and daily requirements.","Created schedules, shift reports and other business documentation to coordinate housekeeping needs.","Collaborated with front desk to respond promptly to guest requests and promote positive experience.","Reviewed employee performance and devised improvement plan to achieve goals."]},{"jobTitle":"House Cleaner","company":"Motel","ttcExamples":["Disinfected bathrooms and eliminated mold and soap scum from shower stalls and bathtubs.","Sanitized kitchen counters, wiped down cabinets and swept and mopped floors.","Performed various laundry duties, including folding, ironing and pressing.","Laundered sheets and removed stains to restore linens to pristine condition.","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"Housekeeper","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Helped prevent spread of infections by sanitizing surfaces, furniture and equipment.","Wiped down surfaces and refilled soap and hand sanitizer to prevent spread of germs.","Disinfected public areas frequently and provided spot cleaning to maintain clean, welcoming atmosphere.","Dusted, swept and mopped to maintain clean, safe environment for clients.","Responded quickly to calls for spills and other potentially dangerous situations."]},{"jobTitle":"Housekeeper","company":"Hotel","ttcExamples":["Completed daily list of rooms to turnover between guests, consistently meeting deadlines and completing thorough work.","Replenished drinking glasses, writing supplies and other hotel amenities to provide elements of comfort and convenience for guests.","Coordinated deliveries of extra room furniture, bedding, linens and towels to meet guest needs.","Informed appropriate facilities personnel of required repairs or upgrades to equipment.","Stored tools in assigned locations, maintaining clean, orderly storage and maintenance habits."]},{"jobTitle":"Housekeeper","company":"Lodging Facility","ttcExamples":["Furnished guests with clean linens and supplied rooms with toiletries.","Reported guest issues, safety and maintenance concerns immediately to supervisor.","Mapped out daily cleaning work assignments by assessing vacant room roster.","Removed soiled linens and articles from rooms and delivered to laundry area.","Polished and sanitized floors, counters, bathtubs and window sills."]},{"jobTitle":"Housekeeper","company":"Healthcare Institution","ttcExamples":["Stocked room attendant carts with supplies to keep carts organized and clean.","Placed housekeeping staff on specific shifts and room blocks based on abilities and daily requirements.","Created schedules, shift reports and other business documentation to coordinate housekeeping needs.","Collaborated with front desk to respond promptly to guest requests and promote positive experience.","Reviewed employee performance and devised improvement plan to achieve goals."]},{"jobTitle":"Housekeeper","company":"Hotel","ttcExamples":["Disinfected bathrooms and eliminated mold and soap scum from shower stalls and bathtubs.","Sanitized kitchen counters, wiped down cabinets and swept and mopped floors.","Performed various laundry duties, including folding, ironing and pressing.","Laundered sheets and removed stains to restore linens to pristine condition.","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance."]},{"jobTitle":"Intern","company":"Consumer Product Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Organized and stored employment forms and information.","Helped with recruitment by posting job openings, screening resumes and scheduling interviews.","Assisted with new hire orientation preparation, scheduling and administration.","Demonstrated awareness, understanding and skills necessary to work in diverse environment.","Worked on multiple projects simultaneously in fast-paced environment."]},{"jobTitle":"Intern","company":"Marketing Services Company","ttcExamples":["Assisted in content research for both internal and external marketing campaigns.","Monitored web traffic to analyze website performance.","Prepared marketing materials and presentations for prospective clients.","Shadowed meetings and observed marketing director to grow professional experience.","Supported team with various administrative duties related to marketing merchandise and promotional programs."]},{"jobTitle":"Intern","company":"Pharmaceutical Company","ttcExamples":["Assisted with investigations and literature reviews to drive initiatives.","Edited reports, communications and background papers prior to publication.","Analyzed experimental data and interpreted results to write reports and summaries of findings.","Designed survey instruments and questionnaires to obtain desired research data.","Interacted with personnel to develop understanding of project needs and requirements."]},{"jobTitle":"Intern","company":"Public Relations Firm","ttcExamples":["Examined analytics to gauge success of campaigns.","Monitored and participated in online conversation to build brand visibility.","Scheduled content for publication on social media at ideal times.","Engaged with and responded to online audience through relevant comments.","Utilized Twitter and Facebook to promote products, services and content."]},{"jobTitle":"Intern","company":"Non-Profit or Local Agency","ttcExamples":["Supported social worker with client case management services.","Complied with HIPAA and confidentiality regulations when communicating with client family members, colleagues and external contacts.","Collected data and entered into internal system database.","Observed therapy delivery, noting treatment models and techniques.","Documented client social history, treatment and related information."]},{"jobTitle":"Janitorial Cleaner","company":"Commercial Maintenance Company","ttcExamples":["Opened and closed building with necessary checks, alarms and door security.","Completed daily cleaning checklists for diverse range of spaces inside buildings.","Serviced kitchen and bathrooms with in-depth cleanings to sanitize spaces and restock supplies.","Checked on building equipment with thorough inspections, handled basic upkeep and reported serious concerns to management.","Handled seasonal maintenance work to keep parking lot and sidewalks free of debris and safety hazards."]},{"jobTitle":"Janitorial Cleaner","company":"Commercial Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Oversaw and facilitated general and preventive maintenance schedule across facility.","Monitored building access and secured premises by locking and unlocking entrances according to established schedule.","Reported or resolved observed hazards observed and followed up to verify resolution.","Established positive working relationships with staff, supervisors and building occupants.","Organized assignments and schedules for subordinates to cover daily and deep cleaning needs."]},{"jobTitle":"Janitorial Cleaner","company":"Healthcare Institution","ttcExamples":["Used correct methods and approved cleaning products to prevent growth of bacteria and viruses on frequently touched surfaces.","Responded promptly to requests to clean and sanitize areas after accidents.","Maintained accountability for keys, master keys and access cards and secured buildings after hours.","Operated equipment according to safety guidelines to prevent damaging property.","Set up furniture following instructions to prepare spaces for events."]},{"jobTitle":"Janitorial Cleaner","company":"Building Maintenance Company","ttcExamples":["Gathered and emptied trash cans and disposed of bags.","Sanitized and deep cleaned bathroom floors and surfaces.","Stored, used and disposed of cleaning chemicals and supplies.","Followed strict schedules, cleaning according to facility usage and room availability.","Wiped furniture and fixtures to remove dust and build-up."]},{"jobTitle":"Janitorial Cleaner","company":"School System","ttcExamples":["Reset school spaces nightly with complete cleanings of bathrooms, hallways and cafeteria.","Detailed carpets weekly around corners, edges and under furniture.","Cleaned glass surfaces daily to remove hand prints and spots.","Re-positioned furniture into standard arrangements for student and staff use.","Dusted surfaces of desks, chairs and tables to maintain cleanliness."]},{"jobTitle":"Kitchen Hand","company":"Chain Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Labeled and stored raw food and ingredients in appropriate storage rooms, refrigerators and freezers.","Substituted for or assisted other cooks during emergencies or rush periods.","Segregated and removed trash and garbage to place in designated containers.","Seasoned food according to recipes or personal judgment and experience.","Operated manual or electric appliances to clean, peel, slice and trim foods."]},{"jobTitle":"Kitchen Hand","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Helped with meal prep for daily meals, following strict sanitation and food handling guidelines","Served specific meals to patients with special dietary needs.","Cleaned and maintained dining room during and after each meal service.","Followed dietary procedures in accordance with established policies.","Stocked food and other supplies for main kitchen and units."]},{"jobTitle":"Kitchen Hand","company":"Educational Institution","ttcExamples":["Kept dishware, glasses and utensils ready for customer needs by quickly scraping, washing and restacking items.","Scrubbed pots, pans and trays by hand or cleaned using industrial washing machine.","Loaded and unloaded dishwashers, washing by hand large pots or items used on continuous basis.","Sanitized counters and wiped down surfaces following food preparation to prevent cross-contamination from raw meats.","Restocked main kitchen areas with items from shelves, coolers and freezers."]},{"jobTitle":"Kitchen Hand","company":"Commercial Cafeteria","ttcExamples":["Re-stocked, organized and arranged service and food stations.","Packaged and stored food products appropriately for proper handling and preservation.","Prepared quality products while maintaining proper food safety practices and presentation within service goal times.","Memorized menu items and food preparation methods to better explain selections to guests and increase sales.","Stored perishable food items in freezer or refrigerator to protect from spoilage."]},{"jobTitle":"Kitchen Hand","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Memorized dining room floor plans and understood seat number system.","Gained broad base knowledge in restaurant operations, both front-of-house and back-of-house.","Assisted servers to optimize guest dining experience.","Responded quickly to customer concerns and escalated major issues to management.","Reset tables between guests, refilled condiments and wiped down surfaces."]},{"jobTitle":"Laborer","company":"Concrete Company","ttcExamples":["Mixed cement and mortar in preparation for pouring.","Prepared and cleaned surfaces for finishing to reduce holes and cracks.","Set up and reinforced forms to accurately pour concrete for walkways and other structures.","Positioned wire mesh and rebar to reinforce concrete.","Finished surfaces by troweling, floating and brushing following project requirements and specifications."]},{"jobTitle":"Laborer","company":"Construction Contractor","ttcExamples":["Maintained clean, safe working environment by removing debris from job site prior to shift completion.","Assisted electrical, plumbing and carpentry teams by completing basic and semi-skilled work.","Used wheelbarrow to move debris and material to designated areas on jobsite.","Installed structures or fixtures using hand or power tools per plan drawings.","Used picks and shovels to dig, spread and level dirt and gravel."]},{"jobTitle":"Laborer","company":"Manufacturing Organization","ttcExamples":["Performed repetitive assembly tasks with hand and power tools and automated equipment.","Collaborated with team members to complete assigned tasks and meet tight deadlines.","Sorted and placed materials or items on racks, shelves or in bins to keep warehouse organized.","Operated pallet jacks and forklifts to load and unload supplies and materials.","Prepared items for transportation installing bracing, padding and strapping to prevent damage."]},{"jobTitle":"Laborer","company":"Landscape Company","ttcExamples":["Assisted in scheduling weekly landscaping projects and tasks to meet deadlines.","Installed block and stone décor according to plans and specifications.","Answered customer questions regarding care and general knowledge of landscape.","Applied chemicals to control weeds, reduce insect infestation and maintain soil fertility.","Trimmed shrubbery and trees to help plants produce more flowers and fruit to benefit wildlife."]},{"jobTitle":"Laborer","company":"Roofing Company","ttcExamples":["Collected and removed debris and roofing materials to disposal areas at end of every shift to maintain clean work area.","Performed skilled and semi-skilled repairs to existing roofs, including shingle replacement.","Unloaded materials to roof by repetitive lifting or through conveyor operations.","Worked regularly at advanced heights and followed all OSHA safety protocols and procedures for fall prevention.","Stayed physically fit in order to climb, squat, reach, bend and lift up to <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> pounds and maintain balance."]},{"jobTitle":"Licensed Practical Nurse","company":"Home Health Agency","ttcExamples":["Administered compassionate care to patients with debilitating back pain, arthritis, fractures, head injuries and strokes.","Supported patients with activities of daily living and functional mobility to improve comfort and quality of life and reduce pain.","Worked with vendors on provision of medical equipment, supplies and services.","Collected biological samples for routine laboratory testing to assist diagnostic processes.","Participated in on-call rotations and delivered after-hours care."]},{"jobTitle":"Licensed Practical Nurse","company":"Inpatient Healthcare Facility","ttcExamples":["Administered medications in accordance with policies and legal limitations.","Educated patients on conditions, medications and self-care skills.","Observed and reported changes in condition of patients and signs and symptoms of deviations from normal health status.","Documented adverse patient reactions to medications and reported findings to supervisors.","Delivered emotional, psychological and spiritual support to patients and families to promote compassionate environment."]},{"jobTitle":"Licensed Practical Nurse","company":"Physicians\' Practice","ttcExamples":["Explained treatment plan care, physician-ordered tests and medications to patients and family members or caregivers.","Assessed need for, ordered, obtained and interpreted appropriate lab tests.","Developed tailored care plans for each patient in collaboration with physicians and healthcare team.","Built trust and rapport with patients by listening to concerns, advocating for wellness and educating on acute and chronic health issues.","Managed pharmacological and non-pharmacological treatment of various disorders and diseases."]},{"jobTitle":"Licensed Practical Nurse","company":"School System","ttcExamples":["Coordinated with families, school personnel and healthcare professionals on behalf of students to advocate for healthcare needs and provide medical information to appropriate parties.","Evaluated students with health concerns or injuries to develop plan of care or provide reference to appropriate healthcare providers.","Administered and supervised administration of prescription medication to students.","Implemented normal growth and development screenings to identify health problems.","Provided direct health care services to students involving triage, evaluation, and first aid care for illness and injury."]},{"jobTitle":"Licensed Practical Nurse","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Observed nurse administration of oral, intramuscular and IV medications to patients as prescribed, monitoring responses for adverse reactions.","Arranged placement of new patient admissions and transfers according to clinical standards and guidelines.","Conducted patient assessments and diagnostic tests to provide physician with important patient health information.","Educated nursing students on proper care procedures and prioritization strategies.","Provided emotional support for patients receiving physically taxing treatments."]},{"jobTitle":"Machine Operator","company":"Parts Maker","ttcExamples":["Kept parts within close tolerances of design standards to maintain optimal quality.","Changed out aging tools, fixtures and offsets.","Observed company\'s strict safety rules during each shift to avoid job-related injuries.","Monitored and adjusted processes or equipment to improve quality and productivity.","Performed routine maintenance on machines and monitored usage to reduce parts breakdown."]},{"jobTitle":"Machine Operator","company":"Data Processing Company","ttcExamples":["Verified accuracy and sorted information to prepare source data for computer entry.","Analyzed and determined source of system errors and malfunctions to determine appropriate resolution tactics. ","Assisted with installation of software updates to computer systems.","Produced accurate and detailed daily reports for processing and measuring progress.","Escalated failures to system and application programming staff for remediation. "]},{"jobTitle":"Machine Operator","company":"Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Inspected equipment and materials for defects prior to operating cranes to prevent malfunction or damage.","Operated mobile crane and moved materials to various locations.","Adhered to OSHA safety standards and precautions including weight capacity, tag lines and ground stability.","Observed and followed signals of those from individuals directing moving and positioning of loads.","Completed assigned tasks accurately and within deadlines to meet site manager\'s specifications."]},{"jobTitle":"Machine Operator","company":"Warehouse","ttcExamples":["Maneuvered forklift over and around loaded pallets, boxes and other materials.","Used handheld scanners for warehouse management system compliance.","Maintained current forklift training and certification as required by company policies.","Communicated with supervisor and other warehouse staff to coordinate work.","Transported material to correct locations and documented inventory changes."]},{"jobTitle":"Machine Operator","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Used care in loading molds to keep materials properly positioned.","Troubleshot press when product defects occurred and immediately remedied issues.","Obtained and reviewed specifications to properly perform job.","Verified dimensions of work piece and made adjustments if necessary.","Promoted safety within department and followed protocols to maximize safety and prevent risk."]},{"jobTitle":"Manager","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Demonstrated excellent communication skills in resolving product and consumer complaints.","Assisted staff with resolving complex customer issues and implementing targeted solutions.","Delivered continuous training to associates to maximize performance and customer relations skills.","Conducted research and reviewed findings to solve customer issues.","Evaluated employee job performance and motivated staff to improve productivity."]},{"jobTitle":"Manager","company":"Business Office","ttcExamples":["Wrote professional business correspondence to maintain strong line of communications.","Trained and mentored administrative staff members in company policies, daily task execution and industry best practices.","Managed office budget to handle inventory, postage and vendor services.","Interpreted and communicated work procedures and company policies to staff.","Reduced financial discrepancies by accurately managing accounting documentation while maintaining case costs and billing processes."]},{"jobTitle":"Manager","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Delivered positive customer experiences by implementing effective quality assurance practices.","Addressed customer concerns with suitable solutions.","Recruited, hired and trained crew members on application of projects, customer relations and customer service.","Directed day-to-day operations by spearheading implementation of short-term and long-term strategies to achieve business plan and profitability goals.","Built strong operational teams to meet process and production demands."]},{"jobTitle":"Manager","company":"Any Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Communicated well and used strong interpersonal skills to establish positive relationships with guests and employees.","Coached team members on food safety and sanitation processes, customer service, menu education and up-selling techniques to drive revenue.","Prepared employee schedules to maintain appropriate staffing levels during peak periods.","Optimized profits by controlling food, beverage and labor costs.","Maintained safe working and guest environment to reduce risk of injury and accidents."]},{"jobTitle":"Manager","company":"Retail Store","ttcExamples":["Strengthened workflow productivity by hiring, managing and developing top talent.","Trained and mentored associates to teach daily tasks and procedures.","Monitored employee performance and identified performance gaps for corrective action.","Managed inventory tracking and physical inventory counts to minimize loss.","Enhanced customer satisfaction and store operations through relationship building and daily problem-solving."]},{"jobTitle":"Marketing Manager","company":"Marketing Business","ttcExamples":["Developed targeted strategies and project plans to drive vision and enhance business value.","Directed social media and digital marketing strategy and initiatives to promote brand building, guest retention and revenue-focused activities.","Gathered analytics data from digital marketing across multiple platforms.","Tracked and analyzed social media and online marketing initiatives.","Supported SEO initiatives to improve content, keywords and branding."]},{"jobTitle":"Marketing Manager","company":"Service Delivery Business","ttcExamples":["Updated web pages and social media profiles with engaging and current content.","Developed and implemented strategic marketing campaigns, including site promotions and engaging digital content.","Executed updated marketing plans to increase branding exposure, customer traffic and sales.","Evaluated and enhanced content of online pages, blog posts and social media platforms.","Developed and deepened professional relationships with vendors, negotiated contracts and monitored performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Marketing Manager","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Developed good working relationships with media and liaised with press on potential news stories.","Developed short- and long-term public relations strategies to improve organization\'s visibility.","Wrote, edited and reviewed various media content and press releases.","Created and implemented communication management strategy, delivering updates as needed.","Updated image and media library and archived older photos and documentation."]},{"jobTitle":"Marketing Manager","company":"Entertainment Company","ttcExamples":["Used editing and graphic design tools to create content and visuals for social channels.","Developed and implemented strategic social media marketing plans.","Tracked social media metrics to determine audience growth rate, volume and reach.","Prepared monthly calendar to manage online content across multiple platforms.","Analyzed market data to determine ways to reach target audience or intended segments."]},{"jobTitle":"Marketing Manager","company":"E-Commerce Company","ttcExamples":["Analyzed market data to determine ways to reach target audience or intended segments.","Prepared professional, on-point and brand-specific copy for diverse platforms and target audiences.","Generated ideas and innovative social media marketing strategies for different brands and platforms.","Leveraged tools to track social trends, identify influencers and devise successful outreach strategies.","Delivered professional and thorough presentations outlining social media strategies and campaign results."]},{"jobTitle":"Mechanic","company":"Airline","ttcExamples":["Researched, read and interpreted technical manuals and guidelines before inspections, installations and repairs.","Performed troubleshooting procedures to find root causes of faults.","Completed scheduled and unscheduled safety and performance assessments.","Managed repair logs, documenting preventive and corrective aircraft maintenance activities.","Utilized drawings and schematics to install, remove and modify aircraft structures, systems and components."]},{"jobTitle":"Mechanic","company":"Car Dealership","ttcExamples":["Performed minor maintenance services, including gasket replacements, coolant flushes and tune-ups.","Completed repairs and maintenance to major vehicle models to meet safety specifications.","Searched within service and maintenance manuals to perform repairs and diagnosis.","Removed, replaced, balanced and rotated new or used tires to maintain on-road safety","Evaluated, repaired and aligned vehicle suspensions."]},{"jobTitle":"Mechanic","company":"Heavy Equipment Repair Company","ttcExamples":["Completed preventive maintenance on engines, transmissions, tires and other vehicle systems.","Performed checklist of fluid levels, air filter, tire pressure and more as part of service orders.","Operated specialty equipment, standard tools and gauges to complete assessments and repairs.","Placed orders for parts necessary to complete vehicle repairs and installations.","Evaluated vehicle systems to assess function and uncover defects."]},{"jobTitle":"Mechanic","company":"Self-Employed","ttcExamples":["Operated hand and power tools to complete repairs.","Repainted walls, removing old paint or wallpaper and preparing surfaces for new applications.","Used professional grade tools and equipment to perform wide range of handyman services.","Built reputation for excellent handyman services by taking pride in craftsmanship and attention to detail.","Kept interior and exterior of buildings clean, safe and welcoming."]},{"jobTitle":"Mechanic","company":"Air Conditioning Repair Business","ttcExamples":["Retained careful and thorough maintenance and repair records in case customers required future service.","Analyzed, modified and repaired digital control systems.","Installed, maintained and repaired commercial refrigeration systems.","Assessed efficiency of HVAC and refrigeration systems to provide feedback to customers.","Examined heating and air conditioning systems and air compressors for signs of defects or malfunction."]},{"jobTitle":"Medical Assistant","company":"Dental Office","ttcExamples":["Sanitized equipment, cleaned treatment rooms and restocked supplies after each patient\'s treatment to maintain cleanliness and prepare for next patient.","Laid out dental instruments and equipment before procedures.","Educated patients on treatment procedures and post-procedure home care.","Gathered and reviewed patient records, data and health history to share with dentists for quick and accurate patient assessments, diagnosis and treatment.","Entered patient data into dental records system and observed confidentiality rules to maintain patient privacy."]},{"jobTitle":"Medical Assistant","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Assisted patients with activities of daily living.","Greeted patients, answered questions and scheduled appointments.","Recorded vital signs, weight and patient information in electronic health records system.","Responded to call lights and completed frequent rounds to meet patients\' needs.","Collected biological specimens and packaged for laboratory transport to complete diagnostic tests."]},{"jobTitle":"Medical Assistant","company":"Medical Practice","ttcExamples":["Cleaned and disinfected exam tables, trays and lamps to comply with infection control policy.","Received and screened telephone calls and visitors by determining or addressing needs.","Submitted diagnosis and procedure codes for insurance companies.","Maintained smooth flow of examinations to keep appointments on schedule.","Communicated with patients to resolve inquiries, schedule appointments and address billing questions."]},{"jobTitle":"Medical Assistant","company":"Surgical Center","ttcExamples":["Processed patient payments and scanned identification and insurance cards.","Applied knowledge of medical terminology and insurance processes to support office administration productivity.","Delivered high-quality administrative and customer service to sustain patient and work flows.","Informed patients of financial responsibilities prior to rendering services.","Straightened up waiting room to maintain neat and organized space."]},{"jobTitle":"Medical Assistant","company":"Medical Device Company","ttcExamples":["Scheduled appointments with established and prospective customers to meet with and discuss corporate offerings.","Demonstrated medical products to new and existing customers.","Established and maintained professional relationships with medical professionals to promote lucrative business opportunities.","Responded promptly to customer calls and emails regarding product issues and complaints.","Input and managed customer data and account information in CRM system."]},{"jobTitle":"Nursing Assistant","company":"Self-Employed","ttcExamples":["Maintained clean and well-organized environment for client happiness and safety.","Supported bathing, dressing and personal care needs.","Improved patient outlook and daily living through compassionate care.","Observed patients for changes in physical, emotional, mental or behavioral condition and injuries.","Followed care plan and directions to administer medications."]},{"jobTitle":"Nursing Assistant","company":"Nursing Home","ttcExamples":["Managed residents\' activities of daily living.","Kept room spaces, linens and restrooms clean and refreshed with supplies.","Supported individuals\' desires for dignity by compassionately assisting with personal hygiene.","Assisted patients with transportation and mobility needs such as moving between wheelchairs and beds.","Assessed patient needs and reported changes or issues to healthcare team."]},{"jobTitle":"Nursing Assistant","company":"Home Nursing Agency","ttcExamples":["Assisted clients with bathing, dressing and incontinence care.","Followed HIPAA regulations to maintain confidentiality of sensitive patient information.","Documented care provided and submitted notes to supervisor.","Managed patient transportation and appointment scheduling.","Helped client with medication self-administration."]},{"jobTitle":"Nursing Assistant","company":"Psychiatric Hospital","ttcExamples":["Worked under supervision of registered nursing staff to deliver quality care to individuals in <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> setting.","Liaised between clinical and admissions teams on patient needs, providing clear communication about goals, progress and needs.","Observed and documented patient behavior accurately in Electronic Health Record (EHR).","Promoted patient safety, monitoring environment and behaviors to proactively identify concerns.","Applied therapeutic communication skills to engage patients, understand concerns and meet objectives of individual recovery plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Nursing Assistant","company":"Home Health Company","ttcExamples":["Redirected poor behavior using positive reinforcement.","Developed rapport to create safe and trusting environment for care.","Assisted clients with personal hygiene, bathing, grooming and dressing.","Engaged clients in age-appropriate activities and playing games.","Collaborated with guardians, physicians and teachers to establish individualized goals and build personalized treatment plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Administrator","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Provided secretarial and office management support while building cooperative working relationships.","Composed correspondence, reports and meeting notes.","Scheduled appointments, meetings and events for management staff.","Monitored office equipment and scheduled repairs.","Utilized editing programs to proofread content for typo-free emails, memos and documentation."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Administrator","company":"University","ttcExamples":["Worked with finance department to file receipts and reimbursements.","Answered phone calls, provided information and connected callers to appropriate personnel.","Executed or delegated tasks to team members to fulfill project requirements.","Gathered, entered and updated data to maintain departmental records and databases.","Delivered reporting, account information and various other tailored data for clients."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Administrator","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Answered telephones to take messages or redirect calls to appropriate colleagues.","Developed innovative strategies to establish best practices, promoting profitability.","Identified and led cost management initiatives to achieve quantified results.","Researched and developed administrative policies, procedures and guidelines to facilitate operations.","Followed up with customer accounts to resolve unpaid or past due accounts."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Administrator","company":"Service Company","ttcExamples":["Monitored calendars and scheduled appointments based on availability and established load limits.","Dispersed incoming mail to correct recipients throughout office.","Collected payments, issued receipts and updated accounts to reflect new balances.","Maintained business records by updating customer information.","Checked office supply levels, anticipated needs and placed orders for appropriate stock levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Administrator","company":"Engineering Firm","ttcExamples":["Wrote professional business correspondence to maintain strong line of communications.","Trained and mentored administrative staff members in company policies, daily task execution and industry best practices.","Managed office budget to handle inventory, postage and vendor services.","Interpreted and communicated work procedures and company policies to staff.","Reduced financial discrepancies by accurately managing accounting documentation while maintaining case costs and billing processes."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Assistant","company":"Convention Center","ttcExamples":["Managed office financial transactions for new payments, deposits and balance transfers.","Supported team with accurate work for wide range of clerical tasks.","Input new data into system, classified information and logged changes.","Served customers with wide range of financial and administrative inquiries.","Maintained accurate counts of cash and general metrics with careful attention to transaction details."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Assistant","company":"Cleaning Service","ttcExamples":["Kept building interiors appealing with routine deep cleaning of high-traffic areas.","Handled, labeled and safely stored various hazardous chemicals and solutions to prevent injuries.","Dusted ledges, countertops, files, office equipment, desks and walls.","Notified building managers about needed repairs to maintain public safety.","Wet and spot mopped to clean floors and other surfaces in public corridors."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Assistant","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Delivered helpful and kind customer service to guests, maintaining composure in stressful situations to maximize customer satisfaction.","Answered multi-line telephone system and routed calls to appropriate personnel.","Sorted and distributed incoming mail, dispersing to appropriate departments and personnel.","Coordinated company records and resources to assist team members with special projects.","Complied with confidentiality regulations in handling customer information."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Assistant","company":"Medical Clinic","ttcExamples":["Supported internal team members with technical knowledge, operational support and exemplary customer service.","Input accurate account data to efficiently update company database and maintain detailed records.","Organized workloads to streamline tasks and efficiently oversee day-to-day operations under tight deadlines.","Managed and distributed incoming and outgoing mail and packages for staff.","Collaborated closely with <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Job title]</span> to effectively smooth and improve office operations."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Assistant","company":"Law Firm","ttcExamples":["Served visitors by greeting, welcoming and directing to appropriate personnel.","Scheduled and confirmed appointments and meetings for management team.","Supervised setup of conference rooms for meetings and office events in common areas.","Oversaw office inventory by restocking supplies and submitting purchase orders.","Screened and verified visitors for identification credentials and purpose of visit to maintain security of personnel and office environment."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Manager","company":"Healthcare System","ttcExamples":["Analyzed financial data to determine efficient use of resources.","Managed financial transactions involving general funds and contracts to reduce cash flow challenges.","Reviewed financial projections relating to business and industry trends and identified areas requiring improvement.","Refined reports and dashboards, providing actionable insight into levels of business.","Compiled and reviewed financial results and operational plans to communicate to company leaders."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Manager","company":"Clinic","ttcExamples":["Maintained and managed filing, chart keeping and organizational systems for practice.","Supervised patient billing, collection and financial counseling and assisted with cash posting.","Oversaw digital patient charting, data entry and administrative duties regarding insurance, billing and accounts receivable.","Developed and implemented office policies and procedures while adhering to HIPAA and OSHA regulations.","Managed staff scheduling and set patient scheduling policy."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Manager","company":"University","ttcExamples":["Interacted professionally with customers and inside personnel, answering questions and responding to phone and email inquiries.","Prepared and made daily deposits and assisted with invoice processing and bank reconciliation.","Reviewed documents and obtained additional information to complete accurate paperwork and avoid delays.","Created memos, letters and other documents, fostering internal and external communication.","Collaborated with administrative support to oversee calendars and prioritize meetings and appointments."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Manager","company":"Law Office","ttcExamples":["Monitored calendars and scheduled appointments based on availability and established load limits.","Dispersed incoming mail to correct recipients throughout office.","Collected payments, issued receipts and updated accounts to reflect new balances.","Maintained business records by updating customer information.","Checked office supply levels, anticipated needs and placed orders for appropriate stock levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Office Manager","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Maintained organized filing system of paper and electronic documents.","Greeted visitors and directed to appropriate location or person.","Sent and distributed mail and parcels.","Coordinated communications, taking calls, responding to emails and interfacing with clients.","Managed multiple calendars and contacts using computer software."]},{"jobTitle":"Officer","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Oversaw budgetary and financial activities and implemented strategies to grow business and profits.","Built strategic business partnerships by cultivating relationships with employees and experts.","Monitored company performance by measuring and analyzing results and minimizing impact of variances.","Led organization by establishing business direction and actualizing operational plans to meet goals.","Drove company vision with collaborative employee engagement techniques and strategic leadership."]},{"jobTitle":"Officer","company":"Bank","ttcExamples":["Answered phone with positive attitude and asked questions to better understand customer needs.","Audited customer account information to identify issues and develop solutions.","Reviewed account and service histories to identify trends and resolve issues.","Educated customers on special pricing opportunities and company offerings.","Handled fast-paced customer inquiries each day to consistently meet productivity and performance targets."]},{"jobTitle":"Officer","company":"Credit Union","ttcExamples":["Adhered to federal and state compliance guidelines relative to retail mortgage lending.","Delivered high levels of customer service to facilitate smooth processes.","Developed and maintained knowledge of available loan products, processing procedures and underwriting and general departmental guidelines.","Performed daily maintenance of loan applicant database.","Obtained and compiled copies of loan applicants\' credit histories, corporate financial statements and other financial information to update credit and loan files."]},{"jobTitle":"Officer","company":"Police Department","ttcExamples":["Patrolled assigned areas both on foot and in motor vehicles, maintaining awareness and providing valuable community surveillance.","Diffused active disturbances with de-escalation techniques, compassion and combat skills.","Communicated with victims, suspects and witnesses to gather and provide information regarding criminal events.","Executed law enforcement patrol functions in assigned locations for extended periods of time.","Issued traffic tickets and wrote incident reports according to commissioner specifications."]},{"jobTitle":"Officer","company":"Security Company","ttcExamples":["Guarded restricted areas to prevent unauthorized entry.","Verified photo IDs and tickets to allow guests passage.","Monitored premises and recorded activity in daily officer reports.","Screened visitors and employees for weapons and contraband with hand wands and metal detectors.","Warned violators of rule infractions and expelled people continuously engaging in suspicious or criminal acts."]},{"jobTitle":"Operator","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Kept parts within close tolerances of design standards to maintain optimal quality.","Changed out aging tools, fixtures and offsets.","Observed company\'s strict safety rules during each shift to avoid job-related injuries.","Monitored and adjusted processes or equipment to improve quality and productivity.","Performed routine maintenance on machines and monitored usage to reduce parts breakdown."]},{"jobTitle":"Operator","company":"Office","ttcExamples":["Assisted with feeding, tagging and treating calves.","Patrolled, inspected and reported animal health and reported suspicious or unusual behavior.","Maintained high standards of animal welfare when performing feeding and milking procedures.","Washed and cleaned cattle udders, milk parlors and tanks.","Collaborated with veterinarians to provide medicine and vaccinations for sick animals."]},{"jobTitle":"Operator","company":"Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Reviewed technical equipment service write-ups and coordinated necessary repairs.","Loaded both raw materials and finished components to support manufacturing and production processes.","Transported materials around construction sites to work locations.","Operated front end loader to move dirt and different base materials.","Inspected and replaced worn vehicle parts to maintain safety and longevity."]},{"jobTitle":"Operator","company":"Warehouse","ttcExamples":["Documented daily production data and submitted accurate time logs to keep management up-to-date.","Organized pallets and secured materials with plastic wrap to prepare for movement to skids.","Established and adjusted feed rates and cutting parameters to keep operations in line with production demands.","Operated multiple fabricating machines, cut off saws, shears and forming or spinning machines.","Manipulated controls to set, activate and adjust mechanisms on machinery."]},{"jobTitle":"Operator","company":"Trucking Company","ttcExamples":["Observed safety protocols and driving laws to maximize road and personnel safety.","Collaborated with dispatch and supervisors to map out routes and schedules.","Reported delays due to breakdowns, weather or traffic conditions and emergencies relating to pick up or delivery of products.","Kept detailed records and driver\'s logs required for compliance with regulations and corporate policies.","Delivered excellent customer service to clients and fellow employees."]},{"jobTitle":"Owner","company":"Entrepreneur","ttcExamples":["Kept records for production, inventory, income and expenses.","Managed operations budgeting, accounts payable and accounts receivable and payroll.","Set pricing structures according to market analytics and emerging trends.","Interviewed, trained and supervised employees.","Promoted business on social media platforms to maximize brand identity and generate revenue."]},{"jobTitle":"Owner","company":"Trucking Company","ttcExamples":["Observed safety protocols and driving laws to maximize road and personnel safety.","Collaborated with dispatch and supervisors to map out routes and schedules.","Reported delays due to breakdowns, weather or traffic conditions and emergencies relating to pick up or delivery of products.","Kept detailed records and driver\'s logs required for compliance with regulations and corporate policies.","Delivered excellent customer service to clients and fellow employees."]},{"jobTitle":"Owner","company":"Software Development Company","ttcExamples":["Outlined new feature plans and specifications.","Collaborated with design team to come up with product look.","Gathered detailed use cases and requirements through regular on-site visits, virtual meetings and customer advisory board sessions.","Advocated for developing critical features in beginning steps to identify and resolve technical issues.","Partnered with software development team to design custom applications and trackers to meet client needs."]},{"jobTitle":"Owner","company":"Franchise Business","ttcExamples":["Located relevant vendors, set up schedules and coordinated delivery, storage and organization of inventory.","Managed food preparation, guest interaction, quality control and customer relations.","Made weekly employee schedules, assigned work tasks and regularly checked quality and productivity of team members.","Administered finances and led business operations by running payroll, making bank deposits and analyzing income and expenses to maintain cost-effective operations.","Hired, trained and motivated staff to fill all restaurant openings."]},{"jobTitle":"Owner","company":"Service Delivery Company","ttcExamples":["Analyzed internal processes and implemented procedural or policy changes to improve operations.","Designed detailed business plans to outline finances, goals and operations of company.","Monitored financial objectives and prepared budgets according to projections.","Controlled shrinkage and product loss with monitoring and inventory management systems.","Trained employees according to specifics of role and company values."]},{"jobTitle":"Package Handler","company":"Shipping Company","ttcExamples":["Drove delivery truck or van to transport orders.","Navigated routes with relevant map programs and GPS systems.","Loaded and unloaded boxes and packages to move to and from vehicle.","Inspected vehicle daily and reported issues to schedule maintenance and repairs.","Carried items weighing up to <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> pounds from vehicle to customer building location."]},{"jobTitle":"Package Handler","company":"Distribution Hub","ttcExamples":["Sorted incoming shipments and separated packages by size, type and destination within warehouse.","Reviewed packing slips and other documentation to properly box requested items for shipment.","Operated forklifts and pallet drivers to move packages and cartons.","Reported safety or workflow concerns to leadership for further investigation.","Trained new employees regarding warehouse procedures and standards."]},{"jobTitle":"Package Handler","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Marked and labeled containers with accurate shipping information to prevent delays.","Assembled customer orders from stock and placed orders on pallets or shelves.","Operated hand trucks, pallet jacks and forklifts to move materials.","Logged packaging activities and filed reports in company databases.","Assembled cartons, crates and containers to prepare for shipping."]},{"jobTitle":"Package Handler","company":"Post Office","ttcExamples":["Set goals and operating procedures that maximized employee effectiveness.","Offered support and advice to newer personnel to improve performance.","Utilized factors such as package shape and final destination to sort into correct bins for delivery.","Supported shipping and receiving needs by loading and unloading transportation vehicles and containers.","Processed payments and handled cash using point of sale (POS) computer system."]},{"jobTitle":"Package Handler","company":"Warehouse","ttcExamples":["Operated forklifts, hand trucks, or other equipment to load, unload, transport and store goods.","Directed warehouse team in stocking merchandise, pulling orders and setting up loads.","Checked items to be shipped against work orders to confirm correct quantities, destination and routing.","Identified order discrepancies and damaged items and notified supervisor.","Prepared packages for shipping and determined most economical shipping methods."]},{"jobTitle":"Painter","company":"Professional Artist","ttcExamples":["Addressed client concerns and worked together to achieve mutually beneficial outcomes.","Selected materials for use based on strength, color and texture.","Met with commission clients to gain agreement on artistic project goals, parameters and financial considerations.","Led classes in community to help individuals embrace creativity and develop artistic skills.","Leveraged accounting software to track income and expenses."]},{"jobTitle":"Painter","company":"Car Dealership","ttcExamples":["Prepared surfaces by removing imperfections, applying rust-resistant undercoats and sealing seams.","Sanded and sealed completed finishes according to precise specifications.","Matched paints to vehicle color specifications or original manufacturer colors.","Readied vehicles for painting by removing accessories and masking surfaces with tape or paper to protect from paint.","Applied color coats using sprayers and brushes."]},{"jobTitle":"Painter","company":"Painting Company","ttcExamples":["Applied paint, stain and varnish to wood, metal, plastic and drywall both inside and outside of residential dwellings using sprayers, brushes and rollers.","Sanded, stripped, brushed and power washed surfaces to clean and smooth, ensuring adherence of paint and primer.","Protected exposed surfaces from harmful substances by setting up drop cloths, plastic or paper.","Received work orders from supervisors and clients to determine scope of work, materials needed and other job requirements.","Primed and sealed unfinished wood, plastic and metal surfaces to prepare for additional coats of paint and other finishing substances."]},{"jobTitle":"Painter","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Inspected components and maintained painting equipment with regular cleaning and basic repairs.","Mixed and prepared paints to meet precise specifications of individual production runs.","Set controls on paint application equipment based on verbal orders and direct production specifications.","Inspected components and maintained painting equipment with regular cleaning and basic repairs.","Balanced speed with accuracy to deliver best paint coverage and meet daily quotas."]},{"jobTitle":"Painter","company":"Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Communicated with crew leader to receive new job assignments.","Mixed paint with additives to create desired results.","Painted walls and other large areas using brushes, rollers and spray guns.","Removed existing wallpaper by applying solution, scraping and peeling paper off walls.","Set up painting job spaces by unloading trucks, placing ladders and laying out protective tarp draping sheets."]},{"jobTitle":"Program Manager","company":"Staffing Agency","ttcExamples":["Communicated project status, requirements and deadlines to stakeholders.","Compiled data for special reports and analyses within prescribed program guidelines.","Assisted management with planning and logistics for program activities.","Drafted agendas, meeting notes and other documents to enhance collaborative process.","Tracked program operating budgets using electronic and web-based programs."]},{"jobTitle":"Program Manager","company":"Community Health System","ttcExamples":["Coordinated logistics for activities and events.","Scheduled and developed program activities in accordance with program needs.","Uncovered issues to determine solutions and assist program participants.","Explained program offerings and requirements to participants and answered related questions.","Developed and distributed brochures, newsletters and flyers for promotional literature."]},{"jobTitle":"Program Manager","company":"University","ttcExamples":["Devised evaluation strategies to monitor performance and determine need for improvements.","Facilitated staff meetings and educational work sessions to strengthen staff competencies.","Wrote proposals and reports for general and specific program support.","Used evaluation outcomes and research to set program goals and determine strategy and direction.","Managed program operations and provided strategic leadership for workers."]},{"jobTitle":"Program Manager","company":"Service Organization","ttcExamples":["Accompanied students on educational field trips.","Supported students in making positive behavior choices and used gentle disciplinary measures when needed.","Implemented play and exploration activities in support of curriculum. ","Spoke at events and distributed fliers to market programs in local community. ","Took roll and reviewed student sign-in/sign-out sheets to monitor safety and absences. "]},{"jobTitle":"Program Manager","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Partnered with program management on recommendations, process improvements and corrective action plans.","Created and implemented strategies to obtain funds for program activities.","Developed and delivered educational and informational presentations on program initiatives.","Identified opportunities to improve or enhance program initiatives and operations.","Gathered statistical data and wrote reports on program outcomes."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Coordinator","company":"Marketing Business","ttcExamples":["Conducted meetings and prepared reports to communicate project status with internal and external stakeholders.","Developed and tracked project milestones to drive on-time and on-budget project delivery.","Liaised with project manager to independently manage smaller projects or contribute to tasks and activities on larger projects.","Maintained close connection with 