ed implementation plans and performed cost-benefit and ROI analyses.","Updated project plans based on changing objectives, specifications and staff availability.","Completed thorough risk assessments and deployed management and response strategies to prevent roadblocks."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Manager","company":"Commercial Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Maintained daily communication with subcontractors and inspectors to drive forward progress of project.","Planned, organized and managed crews and subcontractors through expert communication and handling of work orders and purchase orders.","Completed projects on time and within allocated budget.","Estimated construction costs accurately, achieving consistent business profits.","Interpreted blueprints and plans and relayed information to team of workers."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Manager","company":"IT Service Company","ttcExamples":["Outlined work plans, assessed resources and determined timelines for projects.","Enhanced development and drove continuous improvement of project delivery process by providing strong program leadership.","Designed, engineered and supported various IT projects as key technical resource.","Oversaw budgets for project, tracked expenses and timelines and communicated with key stakeholders on milestones.","Conducted evaluations of hardware and software solutions to develop estimates, negotiate contracts and make effective selections."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Manager","company":"Marketing Business","ttcExamples":["Collaborated with internal teams to develop project solutions resulting in on-time execution.","Prioritized needs and delegated assignments to simultaneously handle multiple projects.","Produced status reports for customers and senior management.","Assessed, monitored and reported on work progression.","Managed portfolio of projects to drive on-time deliverables within scope and budget."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Manager","company":"Engineering Firm","ttcExamples":["Prepared cost analyses, tracked change orders and managed schedules to improve project performance.","Maintained detailed knowledge of internal specifications and design standards as well as applicable regulatory requirements.","Coordinated construction planning, material resources and staff scheduling to achieve on-time, under-budget completion of projects.","Estimated change orders and costs for project manager.","Managed and wrote subcontracts and contracts for various engineering projects across multiple disciplines."]},{"jobTitle":"Project Manager","company":"Luxury Home Builder","ttcExamples":["Oversaw budgets for project, tracked expenses and timelines and communicated with key stakeholders on milestones.","Enhanced development and drove continuous improvement of project delivery process by providing strong program leadership.","Assessed project risks and devised mitigation strategies to avoid potential roadblocks.","Visited locations to observe operations and determine opportunities to streamline processes and achieve cost reductions.","Updated project plans based on changing objectives, specifications and staff availability."]},{"jobTitle":"Receptionist","company":"Dental Office","ttcExamples":["Collected payments from patients and arranged payment schedules.","Arranged documents for insurance claims.","Scheduled cleanings and dental appointments for patients using appointment software.","Answered and managed incoming calls and emails.","Took customer payments and billed insurance companies for remaining balance. "]},{"jobTitle":"Receptionist","company":"Hotel","ttcExamples":["Responded to inquiries and room requests made online, by phone and via email.","Drafted professional business documents, spreadsheets and correspondence.","Handled payment processing and provided customers with receipts and proper bills and change.","Welcomed patrons to front desk and engaged in friendly conversations while conducting check-in process.","Answered multi-line phone system and managed calls by routing to proper extensions or taking messages."]},{"jobTitle":"Receptionist","company":"Clinic","ttcExamples":["Processed patient payments and scanned identification and insurance cards.","Applied knowledge of medical terminology and insurance processes to support office administration productivity.","Delivered high-quality administrative and customer service to sustain patient and work flows.","Informed patients of financial responsibilities prior to rendering services.","Straightened up waiting room to maintain neat and organized space."]},{"jobTitle":"Receptionist","company":"Day Spa","ttcExamples":["Coordinated front desk operations and diligently helped in-person visitors and callers with knowledgeable assistance.","Input client information into booking system accurately and completely to chart sales metrics.","Received phone calls to assist customers in scheduling, rescheduling or canceling appointments.","Satisfied client special requests to enhance patron experience.","Greeted guests and members upon arrival to create positive first impressions."]},{"jobTitle":"Receptionist","company":"Animal Surgical Center","ttcExamples":["Answered multiple line phone system for busy animal care facility and responded to questions regarding pricing and services.","Assisted with new staff training, sharing key information about veterinary practice and protocols. ","Processed financial transactions for clients.","Set up appointments for checkups and scheduled veterinary consultations and surgical visits.","Supervised waiting area, mopped floors and rearranged magazines to maintain office."]},{"jobTitle":"Registered Nurse","company":"Trauma Center","ttcExamples":["Triaged and treated high-volume caseload in busy emergency room setting.","Stabilized patients, determined health needs and provided direct patient care.","Performed triage on incoming patients and determined severity of injury and illnesses.","Maintained open and clear communication with physicians to coordinate effective patient care.","Responded quickly to codes and coordinated efficient and skilled care."]},{"jobTitle":"Registered Nurse","company":"Corporate Hospital System","ttcExamples":["Demonstrated high degree of confidentiality, positive interpersonal skills and adaptability in fast-paced and unpredictable medical environment.","Recorded actions or behaviors of clinical significance in EMR system charts and kept physicians informed.","Deployed therapeutic communication and active listening and teaching to establish relationships with patients, families and health care team for optimum patient care.","Delivered physician-ordered treatments and monitored responses to quickly spot complications and side effects.","Assessed patients using comprehensive evaluation techniques and sound clinical judgment."]},{"jobTitle":"Registered Nurse","company":"Healthcare Corporation","ttcExamples":["Received and investigated complaints from families, patients and clinical staff, devising solutions to multifaceted challenges.","Improved patient outcomes through peer groups and facilitating continuing education.","Applied clinical judgment and comprehensive knowledge of facility policies to assist floor nurses with patient care decisions.","Performed personnel interviewing, hiring, disciplinary actions and dismissals.","Monitored staff performance and provided coaching and formal counseling to staff."]},{"jobTitle":"Registered Nurse","company":"Non-Profit Hospital","ttcExamples":["Developed and maintained professional relationship with members of health care team, patient and patient\'s family.","Helped monitor, maintain and improve nursing-sensitive indicators, core measures and other identified outcome metrics.","Delivered optimum treatments to critical-care patients following prescribed rules, policies, protocol and procedures.","Established and implemented nursing care plans for each patient using protocols of assessment, development, activation and evaluation.","Assessed ICU patients each shift to ascertain vitals and key information."]},{"jobTitle":"Registered Nurse","company":"Birthing Center","ttcExamples":["Briefed next-shift nurses thoroughly on condition, status and needs of mother and newborn.","Prepared and sanitized delivery rooms and instruments and prepared patients physically and emotionally for delivery.","Coordinated overall patient care with specialists, physicians and other departments and supervised ancillary staff.","Discharged mothers and babies after patiently guiding parents through at-home care and follow-up medical care.","Trained and mentored <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> other staff members in obstetrics nursing and care."]},{"jobTitle":"Representative","company":"Business Call Center","ttcExamples":["Assisted customers with inquiries and transactions to meet productivity goals and achieve profit growth.","Navigated through computer systems to review information and respond appropriately to callers.","Offered resolutions to de-escalate calls and solve customer issues.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions.","Made reasonable procedure exceptions to accommodate unusual customer requests."]},{"jobTitle":"Representative","company":"Hotel","ttcExamples":["Promoted high level of guest satisfaction through genuine, enthusiastic and friendly interactions.","Greeted and assisted guests with variety of inquiries, promoting service standards.","Documented guest suggestions and complaints to facilitate process improvements with leadership.","Arranged special accommodations for guests to enhance visitor experiences.","Handled payment processing and provided customers with receipts and proper bills and change."]},{"jobTitle":"Representative","company":"Corporate Hospital System","ttcExamples":["Updated reference materials with Medicare, Medicaid and third-party payer requirements, guidelines, policies and list of accepted insurance plans.","Processed patient responsibility estimate determined by insurance at pre-registration.","Communicated financial obligations to patients and collected fees at time of service.","Applied knowledge of payer requirements and utilized online eligibility systems to verify patient coverage and policy limitations.","Obtained necessary signatures for privacy laws and consent for treatment."]},{"jobTitle":"Representative","company":"Pharmaceutical Company","ttcExamples":["Developed key customer relationships to increase sales.","Leveraged CRM system to manage sales activities and track sales performance.","Answered product questions with up-to-date knowledge of sales and promotions.","Identified customer needs to deliver relevant product solutions and promotions and meet target budgets.","Drove substantial sales through suggestive selling and by promoting add-on purchases."]},{"jobTitle":"Representative","company":"Computer Company","ttcExamples":["Supported customers with online billing, access and account issues.","Served as first point of contact for incoming technical service calls and emails.","Demonstrated advanced product knowledge to solve customer issues.","Used remote login tools to assist clients with technical and product questions.","Assisted customers with various types of technical issues via email, live chat and telephone."]},{"jobTitle":"Runner","company":"Production Company","ttcExamples":["Ran errands to pick up production supplies, food, equipment and props.","Followed instructions precisely related to tasks and errands for multiple individuals, maintaining discretion.","Completed errands within shift time assigned.","Checked totes and bags for completeness of orders before departure.","Shopped for specific items at retail and grocery stores and delivered requests."]},{"jobTitle":"Runner","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Memorized dining room floor plans and understood seat number system.","Gained broad base knowledge in restaurant operations, both front-of-house and back-of-house.","Assisted servers to optimize guest dining experience.","Responded quickly to customer concerns and escalated major issues to management.","Reset tables between guests, refilled condiments and wiped down surfaces."]},{"jobTitle":"Runner","company":"Car Dealership","ttcExamples":["Flexed between counter, delivery and service technician needs daily and maintained proficiency on each area.","Kept parts department professional and well-stocked for customer and staff needs.","Supported service work by quickly distributing parts to technicians and maintaining organized warehouse space.","Completed cycle counts to assist with inventory verification and documentation.","Verified parts against order documentation prior to making delivery runs."]},{"jobTitle":"Runner","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Stayed current on schedules and special events impacting production and completed related preparations.","Retrieved items on- and off-site for personnel, talent and special guests.","Completed opening, closing and side assignments to help keep production on-track.","Supported production by handling administrative needs, preparing show passes and distributing updated guest lists.","Kept production and backstage areas clear of clutter and stocked with commonly used supplies."]},{"jobTitle":"Runner","company":"Big Box Store","ttcExamples":["Counted cash on hand at shift change and closing to determine shortages or overages and prepare bank deposit statements.","Handled escalated customer concerns and emergencies in absence of manager or supervisor.","Supervised and led employees to maintain productivity and customer service levels.","Checked orders for quality and completeness.","Complied with company safety procedures, policies and regulations to promote safe working environment."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Associate","company":"Clothing Store","ttcExamples":["Recovered clothing items from fitting rooms and returned to specified department areas.","Facilitated positive guest experiences by promptly locating desired items for customers.","Performed stock processing by filling and stocking floor racks and backstock racks.","Ticketed items with pricing and markdowns and restocked sales floor according to merchandising plan.","Processed sales transactions using POS system and returned receipts and payment cards to customers."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Associate","company":"Retailer","ttcExamples":["Trained and developed new team members to improve product knowledge and selling abilities.","Organized sales floor to keep products and displays presentable and in sellable condition.","Processed payments and returned receipts, cash, coin and cards to customers.","Maintained awareness of advertised items to accurately recite current pricing and promotions.","Provided leadership and direction to motivate department associates."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Associate","company":"Grocery Store","ttcExamples":["Created price tags and merchandise signs for new items.","Initiated friendly conversation with customers to determine level of assistance required.","Helped customers by answering questions and locating merchandise.","Used product knowledge to suggest items to match client needs.","Calculated pricing, applied discounts and collected payments to process transactions."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Associate","company":"ABC Corporation","ttcExamples":["Built rapport with customers and gave accurate product and service guidance.","Created and managed affiliate partnerships to continue driving sales.","Collaborated with marketing and sales teams to expand brand awareness.","Helped develop profitable go-to-market strategies and related pricing and packaging specifications.","Investigated market conditions to identify priority needs and seek out growth opportunities."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Associate","company":"Pharmaceutical Company","ttcExamples":["Built key customer relationships to increase sales.","Developed customized sales techniques to successfully sell and upsell services to new and existing clients.","Identified customer needs to deliver relevant product solutions and promotions and meet target budgets.","Contacted new and existing customers to outline benefits of products.","Monitored customer order process and addressed customer issues."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Manager","company":"Big Box Store","ttcExamples":["Implemented creative sales and marketing strategies to assist sales team with reaching targets.","Identified prospects to foster growth for new business partnerships to build pipelines.","Prospected, identified and cultivated relationships with contacts to promote product lines and solutions.","Developed and managed regional sales program and market operations.","Penetrated new markets by investigating competitor products, services and trends."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Manager","company":"Retail Store","ttcExamples":["Helped sales professionals finalize customer sales and handled escalated concerns.","Met with team on weekly basis to identify sales opportunities, discuss strategies and execute new promotions.","Developed effective sales team members through highly individualized coaching.","Sourced and onboarded well-qualified inside and outside salespeople to enhance revenue generation.","Collaborated closely with management team to recruit top-level sales talent to fill positions within department."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Manager","company":"Shoe Store","ttcExamples":["Led, coached and developed employees to achieve sales goals.","Supported, trained and motivated team of professionals to consistently meet annual goals for sales and production.","Met regional sales objectives by developing and implementing promotion strategies, coordinating sales team and servicing key accounts to fortify business relationships.","Increased revenue generation by collaborating with senior executives to assess regional performance and develop new sales strategies.","Analyzed quarterly sales statistics and prepared analyses for corporate management."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Manager","company":"Clothing Company","ttcExamples":["Recruited, interviewed and hired talented people offering experience and key selling capabilities to company.","Oversaw daily staffing needs and handled scheduling for store employees.","Mentored employees in management of complicated sales, complex issues and difficult customers.","Greeted guests promptly with positive attitude and asked open-ended questions to better understand shopping needs.","Led employee performance evaluations and rewarded top performers to retain quality personnel."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Manager","company":"Parts Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Exceeded sales goals and improved profitability by aligning sales strategies and business plans with market trends.","Sourced new sales opportunities through inbound lead follow-up.","Communicated regularly with territory and regional managers for daily support and strategic planning.","Contacted current and potential clients to promote products and services.","Developed and maintained records on customer contacts and used information to support effective follow-up opportunities."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Representative","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Improved overall customer purchasing experiences to promote steady revenue.","Built trust and loyalty by maintaining professionalism while persuading customers.","Applied good listening skills to determine customer preferences and financial limits.","Presented sales pitches to clients with basic needs.","Closed sales by building rapport and overcoming objections."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Representative","company":"Medical Device Company","ttcExamples":["Scheduled appointments with medical professionals to sell specific products.","Served as primary contact for named accounts encompassing account management and sales responsibilities.","Analyzed data and market conditions and adjusted sales pitches.","Delivered extensive research and clinical trial data to physicians.","Provided customers with exceptional research and clinical trial data to support product effectiveness and safety."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Representative","company":"Pharmaceutical Company","ttcExamples":["Achieved territory, individual and company goals for call metrics, sample distribution, market share and sales.","Scheduled appointments with medical professionals to sell specific products.","Educated clients on product benefits and provided demonstrations.","Employed effective selling, listening and negotiation skills while communicating with customers.","Implemented and developed strategic business plans."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Representative","company":"Soda Producer","ttcExamples":["Promoted positive relationships with customers to maintain consistent sales.","Utilized corporate vehicle to deliver and sell products to clients with focus on optimizing customer experience.","Continuously surpassed sales goals, optimizing profitability and performance of assigned territory.","Supplied wide range of customers with key products in alignment with specified amounts and schedules.","Maintained positive attitude and diplomacy when dealing with customers and other team members."]},{"jobTitle":"Sales Representative","company":"Product Sales Company","ttcExamples":["Prepared and delivered presentations to position company offerings as best value to clients and prospects.","Expedited customer problems and complaints to successful resolution.","Collaborated with customers to create mutually rewarding and lucrative partnerships.","Developed KPIs with accounts to measure and monitor performance.","Coached and trained peers on selling strategies and product features."]},{"jobTitle":"Server","company":"Conference Center","ttcExamples":["Arranged place settings with clean tablecloths, napkins and tableware to prepare for incoming guests.","Greeted arriving guests and escorted each to assigned tables, took drink orders and answered questions about events.","Collected dishes promptly after each course, cleared crumbs and glassware and maintained customer satisfaction.","Provided exceptional service to high volume of daily customers.","Carried appetizer and drink trays around events and maneuvered around guests and furniture without spilling."]},{"jobTitle":"Server","company":"Coffeehouse","ttcExamples":["Prepared and served cold, hot and <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> beverages to guests.","Backed up cashier staff with processing customer orders and payments.","Greeted customers, answered questions and recommended specials to increase profits.","Checked on dining area to identify immediate needs and reset tables between guests.","Restocked and cleaned counter and service stations throughout shifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Server","company":"Fast Food Drive-in ","ttcExamples":["Handled food safely to protect customers from harmful bacteria and prevent losses or delays from dropped items.","Answered product and order questions accurately and professionally.","Completed orders by making specialty shakes and ice cream desserts.","Independently resolved customer concerns to correct problems and promote brand loyalty.","Reported issues with customers and orders to supervisors."]},{"jobTitle":"Server","company":"Bar","ttcExamples":["Recommended and served alcoholic beverages to patrons during high-volume shifts.","Maintained accurate cash handling practices while efficiently serving customers.","Welcomed guests with personable attitude and brought beverage orders while reviewing menu options.","Communicated with patrons to offer friendly service and determine needs.","Took drink orders from tables and bar area and relayed to bartenders."]},{"jobTitle":"Server","company":"Fine Dining Establishment","ttcExamples":["Investigated and resolved complaints regarding food quality, service or accommodations.","Motivated staff through acknowledgment of hard work and achievements.","VerifIed and confirmed staff schedules to properly cover shifts.","Established standards for personnel performance and customer service.","Provided information about menu selections and made recommendations."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Representative","company":"Bank","ttcExamples":["Built sustainable client relationships built on trust by applying excellent communication and interpersonal skills.","Maintained client relationships and listened to needs and pain points to provide strategic internal feedback.","Collaborated cross-functionally, remaining up-to-date on products, services and policies to inform clients.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions.","Scheduled meetings with prospective and existing clients to optimize long-term business success."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Representative","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["De-escalated problematic customer concerns, maintaining calm, friendly demeanor.","Answered incoming calls and emails, providing frontline customer support or assistance with product and service transactions.","Developed strong customer relationships to encourage repeat business.","Asked probing questions to determine service needs and accurately input information into electronic systems.","Answered inbound calls, chats and emails to facilitate customer service."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Representative","company":"Hotel","ttcExamples":["Promoted high level of guest satisfaction through genuine, enthusiastic and friendly interactions.","Greeted and assisted guests with variety of inquiries, promoting service standards.","Documented guest suggestions and complaints to facilitate process improvements with leadership.","Arranged special accommodations for guests to enhance visitor experiences.","Handled payment processing and provided customers with receipts and proper bills and change."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Representative","company":"Insurance Company","ttcExamples":["Handled calls for new sign-ups, service cancellations and cross-selling opportunities.","Maintained knowledge of company products, services and procedures to better serve customers and meet company goals.","Completed transactions for membership renewals and extensions.","Offered exceptional customer service to differentiate and promote company brand.","Answered member questions about products and services."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Representative","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Accessed patient information through various software applications, maintaining strict confidentiality to remain compliant with HIPAA regulations.","Scanned completed forms, identification and insurance cards, maintaining patient documents folder.","Documented and managed patient information in computer system.","Obtained proper authorization and identification to release confidential medical records.","Scheduled and confirmed patient appointments with patients and healthcare professionals."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Technician","company":"Car Dealership","ttcExamples":["Adjusted, repaired or replaced defective automotive parts.","Inspected vehicles to assess damage and plan for repairs and new parts.","Wrote up detailed repair orders outlining actions and estimated costs.","Tested electronic components and computer controls with specialized devices.","Repaired transmissions, engines, coolant systems and suspension systems on vehicles."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Technician","company":"Cable Company","ttcExamples":["Diagnosed and repaired mechanical issues according to industry standards.","Wrote detailed service reports describing work completed, issues and recommendations.","Operated hand tools and power equipment according to corporate safety procedures.","Trained customers on equipment after installation.","Mentored and trained new employees on processes, flow and safety procedures."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Technician","company":"Mechanic Business","ttcExamples":["Diagnosed and repaired issues with electrical, cooling and suspension systems.","Completed vehicle inspections of brakes, belts and hoses following checklist.","Checked fluid levels to fill and replace at appropriate time.","Lubricated joints and tire rod ends to keep automotive parts fully functional.","Installed batteries, wiper blades and bulbs using appropriate parts."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Technician","company":"Pest Control Business","ttcExamples":["Inspected building perimeters to determine pest point of entry.","Conducted interior and exterior pest control services to alleviate mice and insects.","Followed strict corporate and regulatory protocols governing pesticide and insecticide application.","Recommended company products and services to prevent repeat infestations and boost sales of elimination solutions.","Identified most effective chemicals and treatments for use against specific pests."]},{"jobTitle":"Service Technician","company":"Auto Repair Shop","ttcExamples":["Mounted, balanced and repaired tires for consumer and commercial vehicles quickly, expertly and without need for rework.","Assessed and diagnosed customer needs for tires, services and other products, responded to questions and delivered superior service resulting in repeat business.","Built strong customer relationships through courtesy and top-quality work and earned confidence of customers and management, resulting in <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Result]</span>.","Exceeded customer expectations regularly by beating estimated service times and exceeded employer expectations by outpacing other team members in completed jobs per hour.","Inflated tires to prescribed PSI to meet load requirements."]},{"jobTitle":"Sitter","company":"Self-Employed","ttcExamples":["Monitored children\'s safety and well-being to prevent accidents and falls.","Cared for children of various ages and assisted with feeding, dressing and daily activities.","Helped complete homework, school projects and chores.","Supervised and cared for children ages <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span> to <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Number]</span>.","Organized various activities, games, crafts and outings to keep children entertained."]},{"jobTitle":"Sitter","company":"Direct Employment","ttcExamples":["Maintained clean and well-organized environment for client happiness and safety.","Supported bathing, dressing and personal care needs.","Improved patient outlook and daily living through compassionate care.","Observed patients for changes in physical, emotional, mental or behavioral condition and injuries.","Followed care plan and directions to administer medications."]},{"jobTitle":"Sitter","company":"Pet Care Company","ttcExamples":["Offered animals exercise opportunities through walks and play activities.","Provided seamless communication to inform pet owners of visits and pet status.","Prepared food to meet needs of animals under care with appropriate meals.","Adhered to pet care plans, medication requirements and dietary restrictions as part of quality care.","Promoted optimal animal health by feeding and watering on regular schedule."]},{"jobTitle":"Sitter","company":"Freelance Work","ttcExamples":["Collected mail and packages for homeowners and stored in secure location.","Completed regular household maintenance and chores.","Reported concerns directly to homeowners via phone or text.","Communicated with clients by sending updates and photos.","Maintained yard by watering plants and trimming hedges."]},{"jobTitle":"Sitter","company":"Animal Care Business","ttcExamples":["Walked dogs regularly to promote exercise and maintain proper health and fitness.","Offered every owner exceptional customer service and support as well as top-notch care to each animal.","Noted unusual behavior and contacted owners regarding health-related issues.","Monitored safety of every animal to prevent injuries from other animals or environmental hazards.","Prepared food to meet needs of animals under care with appropriate meals."]},{"jobTitle":"Specialist","company":"Service Company","ttcExamples":["Manipulated data in spreadsheets to reconcile with billing system information.","Investigated and resolved issues to maintain billing accuracy.","Resolved reimbursement discrepancies by analyzing information and notifying manager.","Prepared manual billing data using related billing and service reports.","Input payment history and other financial data to keep customer accounts up-to-date in system."]},{"jobTitle":"Specialist","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Assisted customers with making payments or establishing payment plans to bring accounts current.","Documented customer correspondence in CRM to track requests, problems and solutions.","Resolved customer inquiries, questions and concerns to consistently offer quality service and meet performance benchmarks.","Relayed customer feedback to cross-functional teams to improve products and services.","Improved customer service wait times to mitigate complaints."]},{"jobTitle":"Specialist","company":"Corporation","ttcExamples":["Monitored IT use to maintain compliance with established processes, policies and guidelines.","Oversaw equipment and system operations, surveying for potential security vulnerabilities and upgrade needs.","Maintained working knowledge of current hardware and equipment by completing required training and reading applicable literature.","Removed and replaced old hardware during routine upgrades and system repairs.","Tracked and prioritized IT tickets and requests based on severity and potential business disruptions involved."]},{"jobTitle":"Specialist","company":"ABC Business","ttcExamples":["Collaborated with employees and supervisors to immediately resolve discrepancies in timesheets.","Reviewed, investigated and corrected errors and inconsistencies in financial entries, documents and reports.","Maintained and updated database for invoicing and accounting reconciliation.","Coordinated child support deductions and distributed wage assignments.","Oversaw payroll processing to comply with tax laws and court-ordered wage assignments and garnishments."]},{"jobTitle":"Specialist","company":"Specialty Retailer","ttcExamples":["Stayed up to date on company products and services to support sales objectives.","Educated customers on product features and technical details to highlight benefits.","Calculated production, delivery and installation costs to provide customers with accurate quotes.","Compiled key customer data to plan selling strategies and identify specific client needs.","Negotiated prices and set up contracts to finalize sales agreements."]},{"jobTitle":"Store Manager","company":"Gas Station","ttcExamples":["Coordinated routine responsibilities of staff and allocated resources to meet customer demand.","Monitored employee productivity and suggested improvements for better productivity and service delivery.","Oversaw food and beverage operations in line with health code standards and good practices for consumer safety.","Supervised worker activities to consistently complete opening, closing and daily procedures.","Engaged with customers to check satisfaction with product quality, store cleanliness and service delivery."]},{"jobTitle":"Store Manager","company":"Retail Store","ttcExamples":["Handled shift overstock, restocking and inventory control.","Kept department on-target to meet sales and profit objectives by minimizing waste and pursuing revenue generation opportunities.","Modeled supportive leadership qualities, motivating staff to achieve department goals and promote staff participation and team building.","Supported shrinkage and safety awareness, reviewed sales and inventory data, identified trends and prepared reports for management.","Exercised discretion and judgment in managing fast-paced environment adapting to change with sense of urgency."]},{"jobTitle":"Store Manager","company":"Grocery Store","ttcExamples":["Assessed food store for cleanliness and checked proper stocking of shelves, refrigerated section and freezers.","Analyzed store\'s inventory and ordered merchandise and products to keep stock level.","Coordinated efficient restocking of grocery merchandise to meet customer needs and promote consistent sales.","Distributed daily tasks to appropriate employees and checked to complete duties within expected time frames.","Maintained comprehensive compliance with workplace and food safety standards to protect staff and customers."]},{"jobTitle":"Store Manager","company":"Clothing Store","ttcExamples":["Recruited, interviewed and hired talented people offering experience and key selling capabilities to company.","Built talented and successful team that increased department sales.","Monitored team sales targets and addressed deficiencies.","Mentored employees in management of complicated sales, complex issues and difficult customers.","Oversaw daily staffing needs and handled scheduling for store employees."]},{"jobTitle":"Store Manager","company":"Car Dealership","ttcExamples":["Reviewed inventory levels and ordered supplies to keep products in stock.","Hired and trained service department staff to drive performance.","Created employee work schedules to keep shifts properly staffed.","Prioritized and delegated daily work tasks to meet anticipated project goals.","Created written estimates and obtained customer consent to proceed."]},{"jobTitle":"Superintendent","company":"High-Rise Apartments","ttcExamples":["Planned and managed general repairs and maintenance and construction projects.","Monitored facilities and identified maintenance and repair needs.","Scheduled and assigned work responsibilities to employees to meet shift requirements.","Supervised janitorial and maintenance staff to keep workers on task and complete assignments on time. ","Oriented and trained employees to perform maintenance activities and tasks."]},{"jobTitle":"Superintendent","company":"General Contractor","ttcExamples":["Maintained written daily log of job site activities for permanent records.","Educated employees in proper use of personal protective equipment and enforced safety requirements to minimize workplace accidents.","Maintained project compliance, reviewed contractor scope, secured materials and negotiated pricing for competitive bidding with zero lost time due to accidents.","Eliminated project lags by inspecting work-in-progress to maintain pace, compliance and top quality control.","Supervised residential and commercial new construction and remodels."]},{"jobTitle":"Superintendent","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Determined manpower requirements and scheduled employees in coordination of production activities.","Led and participated in continuous process improvement initiatives.","Recommended machine and equipment modifications to improve production and quality of products.","Provided direction and leadership to shift colleagues consistent with business plan goals.","Coordinated production activities by Planned manpower requirements and scheduled employees in coordination of production activities."]},{"jobTitle":"Superintendent","company":"Commercial Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Developed on-site safety program to support team with risk mitigation.","Defined project deliverables and monitored status of tasks.","Scheduled staff and subcontractors to maintain adequate coverage and complete jobs on time.","Conducted walk-throughs with clients to identify rework needs and answer client questions.","Requested project bids from subcontractors and assessed quotes against budgets."]},{"jobTitle":"Superintendent","company":"Luxury Home Builder","ttcExamples":["Coordinated between vendors and contractors to organize work for minimal delays.","Kept team on-track with close monitoring and direct instructions on job site.","Oversaw work of on-site personnel and tracked upcoming needs to prepare correct materials, equipment and schedules.","Coordinated between vendors and contractors to organize work for minimal delays.","Inspected site daily and documented findings in logs and with pictures."]},{"jobTitle":"Supervisor","company":"Big Box Store","ttcExamples":["Counted tills for beginning of shift with start money and balanced and reconciled register at end of shift.","Greeted customers and responded to requests for information.","Handled customer complaints and concerns and escalated to direct supervisor for quick resolution.","Supported front-end procedures to keep items well-stocked to prevent shrinkage.","Called for backup cashiers during peak times to minimize wait time for customers."]},{"jobTitle":"Supervisor","company":"Call Center","ttcExamples":["Assessed team member performances by delivering one-on-one coaching to promote better service.","Drove positive customer satisfaction levels by providing successful training to associates.","Monitored phone calls to provide feedback and coaching.","Prepared work schedules based on staff availability and forecasted demands to optimize personnel coverage.","Assessed departmental operations to determine areas for improvement and support."]},{"jobTitle":"Supervisor","company":"Manufacturer","ttcExamples":["Maintained clear and safe workspace areas to meet OSHA standards.","Analyzed and identified equipment failure root causes and initiated correction actions.","Collected data to compile detailed reports for upper management and closely monitored equipment, tools and system upgrades.","Inspected alarm systems and monitors to comply with fire, carbon monoxide and other safety levels.","Implemented improved training procedures to better develop new personnel."]},{"jobTitle":"Supervisor","company":"Parts Producer","ttcExamples":["Recommended and implemented measures to improve production methods and quality of products.","Delegated tasks to employees and monitored accurate and timely completion of tasks to meet project milestones.","Conducted performance reviews to identify and rectify areas for skill improvement.","Oversaw continuous improvement initiatives in lean environment to drive gains in quality, flow and output.","Monitored manufacturing variances to achieve quality improvement while resolving product process and equipment problems."]},{"jobTitle":"Supervisor","company":"Distribution Center","ttcExamples":["Monitored daily shipping, handling and receiving to promote smooth operations within warehouse.","Complied with standards and protocol requirements regarding warehouse operations, shipping and receiving and material handling.","Enforced strict safety procedures and protocols through successful management of warehouse team members.","Developed weekly schedules for warehouse employees.","Evaluated procedures, making corrections and changes to reduce safety issues and meet compliance."]},{"jobTitle":"Teacher","company":"Elementary School","ttcExamples":["Prepared daily and weekly lesson plans to help students meet learning goals.","Pursued positive methods to correct student behavior, delivering constructive feedback upon improvement.","Designed and facilitated differentiated and personalized learning goals and activities to engage students.","Embraced and actively promoted inclusive and equitable learning environment.","Cultivated and developed inclusive and equitable working relationships with students, families and staff."]},{"jobTitle":"Teacher","company":"College","ttcExamples":["Guided students to write for varied purposes and audiences to develop writing skills.","Integrated technology into classroom settings to engage students and diversify instruction.","Customized innovative methods and materials to produce effective learning experiences.","Repeated key lesson information to teach grammar and help students grasp concepts.","Identified students\' level of reading difficulty to provide appropriate reinforcement."]},{"jobTitle":"Teacher","company":"High School","ttcExamples":["Developed class learning plans to meet district and statement requirements for instruction.","Established and enforced clear class objectives and requirements to promote consistent education for students.","Promoted safe and clean classroom environment conducive to individualized and small group needs.","Provided individual and small group instruction in order to adapt curriculum to needs of each pupil.","Kept regularly scheduled office hours to advise and assist students."]},{"jobTitle":"Teacher","company":"Middle School","ttcExamples":["Graded tests and papers and uploaded grading information to district system.","Evaluated student academic and social growth and prepared progress reports on individual pupil improvement.","Created and maintained orderly, well-managed and stimulating classroom environment.","Presented subject matter to students in easy-to-understand terms to maximize learning opportunities. ","Coordinated materials and instructional plans for immersive activities exploring concepts."]},{"jobTitle":"Teacher","company":"Preschool","ttcExamples":["Developed professional relationships with parents, teachers, directors and therapists.","Encouraged children to be understanding of others, show good manners and instructed in other social development behaviors.","Collaborated with colleagues on developing new classroom projects and monthly themes.","Incorporated music, art and theater into lesson planning.","Enhanced sensory abilities by giving children access to numerous textures and shapes."]},{"jobTitle":"Team Member","company":"Business Cleaning Company","ttcExamples":["Wiped down various surfaces with approved cleaning products to prevent growth of bacteria and viruses.","Labeled and properly stored chemicals, equipment and cleaning products. ","Measured and mixed detergents with water for use in commercial cleaning. ","Vacuumed floors and dusted furniture to maintain organized, professional appearance.","Dusted ceiling fans and air vents to eliminate dirt buildup. "]},{"jobTitle":"Team Member","company":"Street Vendor Operation","ttcExamples":["Answered customer questions about food preparation, responding to ingredient and allergen concerns.","Modified requested menu items in POS system to customize orders.","Organized food items on serving trays and in carry-out packages.","Processed transactions and made change for cash payments or accepted credit cards, debit cards and gift cards.","Promoted food items, beverages and desserts to increase sales."]},{"jobTitle":"Team Member","company":"Cafeteria","ttcExamples":["Cleaned and sanitized work areas, equipment, utensils, dishes and silverware.","Operated cash register to process cash, check and credit card transactions.","Followed staff performance and service standards to deliver consistent and positive customer experiences.","Controlled portion sizes and garnishing to optimize cost controls.","Sought out and implemented methods to improve food service and team performance."]},{"jobTitle":"Team Member","company":"ABC Landscaping","ttcExamples":["Pruned and trimmed trees and shrubs with shears and pruning saws.","Shoveled snow from walkways to prevent falls and injuries.","Operated landscaping equipment to maintain grounds and remove trees.","Troubleshot mechanical issues and completed basic repairs to keep equipment working at peak levels.","Applied mulch and burlap coverings to bushes and trees for winter."]},{"jobTitle":"Team Member","company":"Warehouse","ttcExamples":["Monitored key performance indicators throughout shipping and receiving cycles.","Oversaw delivery, packaging and shipment for material transitioning from warehouse to customer location.","Managed accurate inventory counts in internal supply chain systems.","Advocated for accident preparedness and safety training to maintain safe working conditions.","Reconciled invoices with service requests and inventory verification."]},{"jobTitle":"Technician","company":"XYZ Corporation","ttcExamples":["Consulted via telephone to understand user problems, run through testing scripts and ask probing questions to locate root causes.","Installed software updates and vulnerability patches on servers to prevent possible threats from penetrating networks.","Performed troubleshooting on networking and connectivity issues to restore connections and network access.","Advised customers and users on required maintenance practices for diverse software systems to support OEM warranty requirements and industry best practices.","Set up new desktop systems and configured laptops for incoming employees and loaded required software and server permissions."]},{"jobTitle":"Technician","company":"Research Laboratory","ttcExamples":["Maintained, cleaned, and prepared lab instruments for cell cultures.","Executed daily tests to assist managers and operators with processes.","Performed daily housekeeping tasks driving efficient laboratory operations.","Managed laboratory supplies and equipment, providing maximum output to meet data deadlines.","Collected, labeled and stored lab samples according to laboratory specifications."]},{"jobTitle":"Technician","company":"High-Rise Complex","ttcExamples":["Collaborated with building managers to assess ongoing needs and plan preventive maintenance schedules.","Installed machinery and equipment according to blueprints and layout plans.","Diagnosed problems with mechanical and electrical systems and equipment using advanced troubleshooting abilities.","Cleared clogged drains and replaced valves, faucets and fixtures.","Installed new systems, replacement parts and components to maintain proper operation."]},{"jobTitle":"Technician","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Monitored patient therapy responses, reporting concerns to supervisor.","Supported healthy patient skin with bedside baths, wound care and integrity checks.","Delivered outstanding patient care based on physical, psychological, educational and related criteria.","Restocked unit frequently with necessary medical supplies.","Transported patients to other areas of hospital in wheelchairs and gurneys for tests, treatments and therapies."]},{"jobTitle":"Technician","company":"Office Equipment Company","ttcExamples":["Conducted service appointments to diagnose and fix problems.","Followed established safety rules, OSHA guidelines and company safety policies and procedures.","Communicated with clients for outstanding customer service and to increase repeat business.","Implemented troubleshooting tactics to identify causes of poor machine performance.","Reconditioned and repaired machine systems and components to return to operation."]},{"jobTitle":"Technologist","company":"Clinic","ttcExamples":["Followed proper procedures for working area with ionizing radiation and high magnetic fields.","Completed CT scans and related patient care procedures using age appropriate methods for patient\'s physical ability and individual limitations.","Operated CT equipment to generate quality images and troubleshot problems.","Acquired accurate patient history and documented details in medical record.","Placed IVs to prepare for injection of contrast media."]},{"jobTitle":"Technologist","company":"Off-Site Laboratory","ttcExamples":["Tested samples within required timeframes and following appropriate standards, logging results in files.","Handled and disposed of chemicals, reagents and biological samples in compliance with applicable regulations.","Prepared and used correct controls for tests and recognized out-of-range results, shifts and trends.","Investigated and troubleshot problems with equipment to diagnose malfunctions and complete basic maintenance.","Completed regular checks and documented use dates for controls, reagents and calibrators."]},{"jobTitle":"Technologist","company":"On-Site Laboratory","ttcExamples":["Evaluated body fluids and tissue samples to document findings such as normal or abnormal results.","Used microscopes and cell counters to perform assigned tasks.","Communicated with physicians to discuss lab test findings, procedures and other relevant information.","Supported quality control processes by monitoring activities and reporting.","Documented medical test data and results in patient medical records."]},{"jobTitle":"Technologist","company":"Hospital","ttcExamples":["Reduced exposure to radiation using beam-restrictive devices and patient shielding techniques.","Instructed and prepared patients to facilitate x-ray or other examinations.","Determined suitable anatomical positions and shielded patients to avoid injuries.","Utilized sterile technique when performing invasive procedures, reducing infection.","Set up sterile tables and prepared patients using aseptic techniques."]},{"jobTitle":"Technologist","company":"Outpatient Surgery Center","ttcExamples":["Reviewed surgical requirements and prepped operating room with appropriate tools, equipment and instruments.","Organized equipment and instruments in alignment with surgical protocols and surgeon preferences.","Assessed procedure requirements and procured appropriate equipment and tools.","Assisted surgeon by passing instruments and sterile supplies throughout operation.","Recounted surgical instruments and supplies at end of operation, eliminating chance of items left inside patient."]},{"jobTitle":"Volunteer","company":"No-Kill Animal Shelter","ttcExamples":["Maintained animal shelter by cleaning and disinfecting kennels, cages and equipment, washing dishes and laundry, taking out garbage and performing custodial duties.","Performed daily feeding and watering and cleaned animal enclosures for rescued animals.","Cleaned kennel and offices areas by mopping, sweeping and sterilizing equipment.","Assisted with bathing and brushing to keep animals clean, attractive and comfortable.","Helped visitors to select and adopt appropriate animals based upon needs and requirements."]},{"jobTitle":"Volunteer","company":"ABC Church","ttcExamples":["Assisted with childcare and enabled parents to attend church services without distraction.","Encouraged and engaged with congregation and visitors to promote church mission.","Fostered warm and welcoming community to nurture youth and inspire life of discipleship.","Leveraged talents and background to aid and fulfill church needs with service and actions.","Worked in church office to answer telephone calls and organize records."]},{"jobTitle":"Volunteer","company":"Community Food Bank","ttcExamples":["Boxed family-sized boxes of groceries for distribution to families in need.","Sorted and packaged items to be delivered to clients.","Assisted with stocking shelves and removing expired items.","Facilitated positive, grocery store atmosphere for clients visiting food bank.","Repackaged bulk donations into smaller portions for distribution."]},{"jobTitle":"Volunteer","company":"Urban Hospital","ttcExamples":["Answered visitor questions, offered directions and escorted to destination.","Sat with patients in need of companionship and emotional support.","Transported laboratory results, biological specimens and patient records to correct locations.","Restocked bins and shelves and displayed newest merchandise.","Provided reception support and gave general information to visitors and families."]},{"jobTitle":"Volunteer","company":"Any Library","ttcExamples":["Assisted with special events such as book groups, coffee clubs and storytime for children.","Organized circulation of library materials.","Updated website with current and relevant information.","Helped patrons find specific materials, access library technology and learn borrowing policies.","Worked alongside library staff to shelve books and organize collections."]},{"jobTitle":"Waiter","company":"ABC Bar","ttcExamples":["Calculated charges, issued table checks and collected payments from customers.","Communicated with hosts, bussers and kitchen staff to prepare for and serve customers.","Monitored patron alcohol consumption to encourage safety.","Recommended food and drinks to patrons based on preference, pairings and special promotions.","Created rapport with new and returning patrons to foster guest satisfaction."]},{"jobTitle":"Waiter","company":"Casual Dining Establishment","ttcExamples":["Maintained accuracy while handling payments, giving change and printing receipts for customers.","Communicated with kitchen staff to stay updated on item availability and customer wait times.","Completed opening and closing checklists to ensure smooth restaurant operations.","Increased beverage sales with food and drink pairing suggestions to suit unique customer preferences.","Stocked server areas with supplies before, during and after shifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Waiter","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Maintained knowledge of menu items, ingredients and preparation methods to assist guests with menu selection.","Trained new wait staff team members in proper procedures and important standards of establishment.","Rolled silverware and set up food stations and dining areas to prepare for next shift or large parties.","Greeted customers, answered questions and recommended specials to increase profits.","Met with chefs to collaborate on menu changes, staffing needs and ways to improve restaurant."]},{"jobTitle":"Waiter","company":"Fine Dining Establishment","ttcExamples":["Set tables with correct arrangements of dishes, glassware and silverware.","Set up according to table plan, cover layout and standards defined by management.","Anticipated guest needs, ascertained satisfaction, and responded urgently to guest concerns and requests.","Balanced large platters and serving bowls to bring food items to tables and serve guests.","Loaded cart with multiple serving dishes and organized smooth, professional service to guests."]},{"jobTitle":"Waiter","company":"Cafeteria","ttcExamples":["Answered guest questions regarding menu, food and beverage preparation, recipe ingredients and allergens.","Cleared table and bussed dishes to allow for quick setups.","Set up dining room to meet hospitality and service standards.","Greeted newly seated guests promptly, filled water glasses and brought bread to table.","Handled special customer requests for separate checks and menu substitutions."]},{"jobTitle":"Waitress","company":"Fine Dining Establishment","ttcExamples":["Delivered VIP bottle service in upscale environment, catering to large guest parties and celebrity clientele.","Managed reservations, parties and events to coordinate special occasions for guests.","Assembled VIP bottle service kits with garnishes, mixes and bottles to solicit to guests.","Recommended menu items to complement cocktails and beverages.","Interacted casually with customers, taking drink and bottle orders."]},{"jobTitle":"Waitress","company":"Bar","ttcExamples":["Calculated charges, issued table checks and collected payments from customers.","Checked identification to verify minimum age requirements for consumption of alcoholic beverages.","Created rapport with new and returning patrons to foster guest satisfaction.","Suggested cocktail choices based on customer preference, daily specials and inventory availability.","Took drink orders from tables and bar area and relayed to bartenders."]},{"jobTitle":"Waitress","company":"Coffeehouse","ttcExamples":["Prepared and served cold, hot and <span class=\'ttc_token\'>[Type]</span> beverages to guests.","Backed up cashier staff with processing customer orders and payments.","Greeted customers, answered questions and recommended specials to increase profits.","Checked on dining area to identify immediate needs and reset tables between guests.","Restocked and cleaned counter and service stations throughout shifts."]},{"jobTitle":"Waitress","company":"Catering Company","ttcExamples":["Worked multi-course dinners with pre-plated foods.","Set up and tore down food and beverage services in banquet halls and at customer locations.","Stocked drink, buffet and condiment stations prior to events.","Carried trays of beverages, food items, and hors d\'oeuvres around events.","Responded quickly to guest requests and delivered desired items or drinks."]},{"jobTitle":"Waitress","company":"Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Maintained knowledge of menu items, ingredients and preparation methods to assist guests with menu selection.","Trained new wait staff team members in proper procedures and important standards of establishment.","Rolled silverware and set up food stations and dining areas to prepare for next shift or large parties.","Greeted customers, answered questions and recommended specials to increase profits.","Met with chefs to collaborate on menu changes, staffing needs and ways to improve restaurant."]},{"jobTitle":"Warehouse Worker","company":"Manufacturing Company","ttcExamples":["Contributed to team-based environment to maintain line productivity and meet expected deadlines.","Used established assembly instructions to complete jobs.","Recognized defective material and reported issues to management.","Boxed, labeled and moved items to keep production lines moving swiftly.","Built and packaged products to comply with multiple work orders and deadlines."]},{"jobTitle":"Warehouse Worker","company":"Distribution Center","ttcExamples":["Maneuvered forklift over and around loaded pallets, boxes and other materials.","Used handheld scanners for warehouse management system compliance.","Maintained current forklift training and certification as required by company policies.","Communicated with supervisor and other warehouse staff to coordinate work.","Transported material to correct locations and documented inventory changes."]},{"jobTitle":"Warehouse Worker","company":"Logistics Company","ttcExamples":["Coordinated inventory, stocking and ordering.","Participated in physical inventory counts to keep information accurate and current.","Utilized tracking systems to verify cargo routes and delivery dates.","Ran analytics, producing forecasts to determine inventory needs.","Oversaw efficient receiving and inventory management to keep stock within optimal levels."]},{"jobTitle":"Warehouse Worker","company":"Any Warehouse","ttcExamples":["Operated forklift to move inventory items.","Loaded completed orders on pallets according to delivery numbers.","Packed merchandise into boxes and containers in preparation for safe shipment.","Unloaded cargo from trucks with mechanized equipment.","Logged unit quantities and entered data into inventory database."]},{"jobTitle":"Warehouse Worker","company":"Shipping Company","ttcExamples":["Confirmed items picked for orders by keying codes into system.","Reviewed packing slips and other documentation to properly box requested items for shipment.","Marked and labeled containers with accurate shipping information to prevent delays.","Weighed and measured products and materials to meet regulatory requirements.","Selected products and items from shelves and pallets for customer orders."]},{"jobTitle":"Worker","company":"Construction Company","ttcExamples":["Maintained clean, safe working environment by removing debris from job site prior to shift completion.","Assisted electrical, plumbing and carpentry teams by completing basic and semi-skilled work.","Used picks and shovels to dig, spread and level dirt and gravel.","Read plans, instructions or specifications to determine work activities.","Built and disassembled scaffolds, bracing and barricades to assist in vertical construction activities."]},{"jobTitle":"Worker","company":"ABC Farm","ttcExamples":["Repaired buildings, fences and other pertinent structures to keep animals properly contained.","Watered and fed livestock and cleaned pens and enclosures to maintain farm animal health.","Drove trucks and tractors to distribute feed to animals.","Moved livestock to pastures for grazing or to scales and enclosures.","Sprayed fertilizer or pesticide solutions to control insects and fungus."]},{"jobTitle":"Worker","company":"Fast Food Restaurant","ttcExamples":["Greeted customers to take food orders and provide information about menus.","Operated cash register and received payment from customers in cash or credit form.","Received inventory of food and beverage products to stock in designated areas.","Organized food items on serving trays and in carry-out packages.","Modified requested menu items in POS system to customize orders."]},{"jobTitle":"Worker","company":"Any Maintenance","ttcExamples":["Operated hand tools and power tools to make minor maintenance repairs and maintain grounds and walks.","Identified problems during daily work inspections and addressed concerns.","Removed snow from sidewalks, driveways, and parking areas.","Notified management about necessary repairs or professional service needs for building operating systems.","Followed correct procedures for handling, transporting and disposing of new and recycled materials."]},{"jobTitle":"Worker","company":"School Office","ttcExamples":["Followed instructions from management to complete tasks according to exact specifications.","Answered phone calls and took messages or transferred to appropriate parties.","Assisted with different events during fall and spring semesters.","Routed incoming mail and prepared outgoing mail according to campus procedures.","Maintained and updated filing and inventory systems using computer databases."]}]')},1096:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"nm":"Flow 1","h":88,"w":88,"meta":{"g":"LottieFiles Figma v106"},"layers":[{"ty":4,"nm":"Searching and creating bullets animation","sr":1,"st":0,"op":68.12,"ip":0,"hasMask":false,"ao":0,"ks":{"a":{"a":0,"k":[44,44]},"s":{"a":0,"k":[100,100]},"sk":{"a":0,"k":0},"p":{"a":0,"k":[44,44]},"r":{"a":0,"k":0},"sa":{"a":0,"k":0},"o":{"a":0,"k":100}},"shapes":[],"ind":1},{"ty":4,"nm":"Frame","sr":1,"st":0,"op":68.12,"ip":0,"hasMask":false,"ao":0,"ks":{"a":{"a":1,"k":[{"o":{"x":0.33,"y":1},"i":{"x":0.68,"y":1},"s":[65.5,34.8],"t":0},{"o":{"x":0.33,"y":1},"i":{"x":0.68,"y":1},"s":[40,34.8],"t":18},{"h":1,"o":{"x":0.167,"y":0.167},"i":{"x":0.833,"y":0.833},"s":[52,34.8],"t":36},{"h":1,"o":{"x":0.167,"y":0.167},"i":{"x":0.833,"y":0.833},"s":[52,34.8],"t":6